\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Fol, Yesu Kerisoene faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r, n\u233?namndai Yesuene muyaf\u233? \u225?r a f\u233?nataye n\u225?y\u225?toi Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mer si waitogh\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam uny\u233?ghofnar si yiy\u225?toi y\u233?n\u233? mer si t\u225?nd\u225?i, soram\u233? nufrotam. Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r\u233?m y\u233?farotaw\u233?t y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n Bukan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? mer si siy\u233?m y\u225?njo Ambumoenem\u233?n, f\u225? n\u225?r\u225?ftam Deifidene m\u233?rnan fifie. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
A njam nanoi k\u233?rta m\u233?naye Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r waftaye, f\u225? t\u233? yuyafoi s\u225?i t\u233?morw\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene Ambum Yesu Keriso t\u233?fene Yur\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Y\u225? k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?nmaramai ng\u225?r\u225?m Kerisoene y\u233?tkw\u233?n t\u233?fnan y\u225?ne muyaf\u233? \u225?r, m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i elimndam T\u233?ndo \u225?r \u225?y\u225?rgh\u233?t \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?n\u233?m k\u233?tam\u233? ndimbal mwighata. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
F\u233?m w\u233?i f\u233?t\u233? em y\u233?fefaf, efe t\u233? n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?nd Yesu Kerisoene.
