Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne y\u233?ndon yaus\u225?fotan tane tikfe m\u233?n\u225?yan y\u225?ne Ambumoene si waitoghan, f\u225? siy\u233?m tane gh\u233?k\u233?f fayogh \u225?r ndern\u225?ye ekmboghofnar y\u233?ndon ewafarotan f\u233?m {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
tane Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oray\u233?gh k\u233?nj\u250?n m\u233?nyotio efghon. A y\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? noraiwam nden\u233? s\u233?nonjo soram\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene m\u233?ndeyan end so kasaw\u233?rng\u233? tayot s\u225?i w\u233?n\u233?m f\u233?fefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Y\u233?nd minde m\u233?nde w\u233?m f\u233?fe fandagh\u233?t, m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?ndon so ef\u233?rmetan f\u233?fefaf \u225?mb mb\u233?rmb\u233?re tamb\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t so t\u225?y\u225?tong\u233? muyaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u233?m a y\u233?nd s\u225?i naw\u225?ut\u225?nam mere t\u233?fene ndimbal mwighaye.
