Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene n\u233?kw nufrote njafarta y\u233?fefaf m\u233?inyotio ng\u225?nj\u225?nofnar gh\u233?rsaf\u233? \u225?r a yaufiyam wafrogh t\u233?fn\u225?r emofem yengwitrotat efalo y\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?ta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
F\u225? so f\u233?t\u233? mat em Ng\u225?nj\u225?n efe y\u233?m, m\u233?nam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?namyo t\u233? ewauyafoi s\u225?fotro y\u233?feyot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
K\u233?tam\u233? mband marat nufrotam, \u225?r\u233?m t\u233? yinjoy\u233?nd mband a njafar. Y\u233?nayan m\u233?inyotio rokar Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ewafrotam, y\u233?mofem f\u233?yotaro so efandat saf\u233?nro y\u225?ne fandaghofnar yam, y\u225?ne akegh waft\u233? a m\u233?nde. F\u233?yo k\u233?t\u233? \u225?mb yau endeyot si y\u233?m s\u225?i noraya, y\u233?nd yau mat t\u233?nmorw\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nenem\u233?n efaloyam.
