Ndemam\u233?n f\u225? mat em Ng\u225?nj\u225?nenem\u233?n, w\u233?nde y\u233?mofem yau kor t\u225?wefnotaw\u233?t nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, o yau kor tarametaw\u233?t k\u225?njo si y\u225?faf. W\u233?nde f\u225? yau kor kemnaw\u233?t saf\u233?nro. Y\u233?fene mwigh\u233? n\u233?namnday\u233?nd kw\u233?fitayan a orsaghan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Ndemam\u233?n f\u225? namndetat k\u225?fet\u233? \u225?r em, w\u233?nde f\u225? em mwigh\u233?mwighafnar; {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Y\u233?mofem y\u233?kenat s\u225?i y\u225?wefnotat ndimbal Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne efe yau so k\u233?r y\u233?m. W\u233?nde, y\u233?mofem ewafrotat uny\u233?gh ng\u225?nj\u225?n y\u233?fendio. Y\u233?mofem ew\u225?wefnotat mewangat \u225?rk\u233? em \u225?rnit efe k\u233?r so em. Y\u233?mofem w\u233?i ewafrotat \u225?rk\u233? n\u233?r\u233?tat mennit, w\u233?r\u225?rnit a kambannit, a y\u233?mofem ew\u225?wefnotat.
