Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam eramai k\u233?t\u225?n w\u225?iw\u225?iaf\u233? m\u233?nde yam wafrogh\u233?t. Y\u233?fene amafam yengoy\u233?nd \u225?rf\u233? k\u233?m\u233?gh yam k\u233?t\u225?n amafro k\u233?m\u233?gh yamfaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Nden\u233? yameyo \u225?r\u233?m y\u233?frangoy\u233?nd amafaf\u233? k\u233?m\u233?gh yam a nufngoy\u233?nd \u225?r ghak\u233?r ro yam f\u225?rof\u225?ro. \u193?r w\u225?iw\u225?iaf\u233? yam nefngoy\u233?nd f\u225?rof\u225?ro, a yanay\u233?nd fai y\u233?fenjo yaufim\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
T\u225?f y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r nakenay\u233?nd s\u225?i tafarotaw\u233?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, f\u233?yo Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam eumyoi y\u233?fene mwigh\u233? ewas\u233?rmbotam. F\u233?yo y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan, y\u233?mofem tawafrotaw\u233?t yaufi yam \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? yau so tawafrotaw\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
F\u225? t\u233? ewafoi m\u233?inyotio f\u233?nat\u233? \u225?y\u225?r\u233?ghofnar yamam, yaufi, nit\u233? a m\u225?m\u225?fi. F\u225? sem waramnjaghro, ngi, \u225?sm\u233?gh, wasogh a \u225?r fayogh. F\u225? sem si tiy\u225?r\u233?gh, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
a uny\u233?gh si wafrogh \u225?rfenem\u233?n, Ng\u225?nj\u225?n m\u233?ndm\u233?nd, utman\u233?ghofnar, ndimbalndimbal mwigh\u233?, a awarmbogh mwigh\u233?. Y\u233?mofem nemnat t\u225?rf\u225?r ende yaufi wafrogh\u233?t, a y\u233?mofem yau ey\u225?retat y\u233?ferafaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
F\u225? yau mat em n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?m mbark\u225?nd. Y\u233?mofem er\u225?fnat y\u233?fene uny\u233?ghofnar si. Y\u233?mofem yau euwetat \u225?mb \u225?r a yau em gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? \u225?mb \u225?rfefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
F\u225? mat em Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mbark\u225?nd yam y\u233?nat emofem ewafrotat y\u233?n\u233? yam so em k\u233?r. W\u233?nde y\u233?mofem m\u233?njtaye m\u233? ewafrotat y\u233?n\u233? yaufi yam. Minde m\u225?m\u225?fiot, y\u233?mofem ewawanjat \u225?mb \u225?r m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i ewafrotat w\u233?i.
