Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n, f\u233?m m\u233? nemne f\u233?m s\u225?i moghan ekmeta nden\u233? \u225?r, w\u233?nde f\u233?m nden\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fiyo n\u233?m, a f\u233?feyot \u225?mb yau so n\u233?m uwangogh! Njam f\u233?m noraye f\u225? em yaufi a so t\u233?kratan em, f\u233?m f\u233?myo moghan nakmeta, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mo emofem njam moghan ekmeta \u225?mb \u225?r ewafrote y\u233?n\u233? yamyo w\u233?i. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
