F\u233?mo y\u233?f\u233?rmete \u225?mogh y\u233?fefaf a ewafrote w\u233?i y\u233?n\u233? yamyo. F\u233?m nemne so k\u225?tnongi Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene moghta? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
