Njam Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam uny\u233?ghofnar sie noyarai Ebraam nden\u233? f\u225? so k\u233?namndang\u233? y\u233?feraf\u233? mband maratoene, Ebraam\u233?m efalo tiy\u225?totau f\u225?. Ng\u225?nj\u225?n w\u233?i t\u233? norayai, "Fene \u225?kiambum so em nden\u233? wafoghofnar k\u233?nd." Y\u225?ne m\u233? y\u233?m m\u233?ghm\u233?gh njam yau y\u225?ne y\u233?m mer t\u233?f\u233?n m\u233?ghm\u233?ghot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Ebraam t\u233? n\u233?namndai nden\u233? 100 yunj\u233?f. Y\u225?ne fifi n\u233?namdai bulu. Y\u225?ne amafaus\u233?, Sara w\u233?i nden\u225?yo f\u233?yotarofnar t\u233?morw\u233?n ambum unjgh\u233?t. Ebraam mat m\u233?inyotio t\u233?morw\u233?n y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n, w\u233?nde f\u225? yau n\u233?kmboi Ng\u225?nj\u225?n wafarogh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
F\u225? yau k\u233?kmbongai efalo y\u225?togh\u233?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene uny\u233?ghofnar sian. W\u233?nde y\u233?mo efalo tiy\u225?totau Ng\u225?nj\u225?n minde muyaye. Y\u233?mo efalo tiy\u225?totau Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ndimbal waft\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Ebraam efalo yiy\u225?toi nden\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so tawafrotau n\u233?mat f\u225? uny\u233?ghofnar si y\u233?mndai wafrogh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n y\u233?ndfem y\u233?fandam nden\u233? y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m efalo: M\u233?nam\u233?n Ebraamene ndimbal mwigham\u233?n, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yumyoi f\u225? nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? mbark\u225?ndro y\u233?maf\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Nemnati y\u233?n\u233? sim\u233?n, 'Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yumyoi f\u225? nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u225? mbark\u225?ndro y\u233?m. F\u225? yau y\u225?nem\u233?nro norayat Ebraam, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
w\u233?nde w\u233?i t\u233?feyot. Njam y\u233?ndfem efalo yiy\u225?totam Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, y\u233?mo so t\u233?nmumyong\u233? y\u233?nd nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? mbark\u225?ndro y\u233?maf\u233?. Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yanoi k\u233?rta t\u233?fene Yur\u233? Yesu, m\u233?n\u225?t f\u225? n\u233?namndai gh\u233?rsat w\u233?ikor y\u225?ne k\u233?r soram\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam eumyoi \u225?r y\u233?smetam\u233?nd Yesu wafatar\u233?gh w\u233?nan t\u233?fene yaufiyamm\u233?n. F\u233?yo Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yanoi Yesu k\u233?rta, m\u233?n\u225?t yuyafoi nden\u233? y\u233?mo so y\u233?nd t\u233?nmumyong\u233? nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? mbark\u225?ndro y\u233?maf\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 5
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Krufr\u225?t a m\u233?ghm\u233?gh
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde, y\u233?nd efandam nden\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n t\u233? y\u233?nmumyoi y\u233?nd nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? mbark\u225?ndro m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?ndfem efalo yiy\u225?totam f\u225?. Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan, t\u233?fefaf y\u233?m krufr\u225?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? m\u233?nam\u233?n n\u233?m\u233? t\u233?fene Yur\u233? Yesu Kerisom t\u233? yafrotam t\u233?feyot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
T\u233?fene ndimbal mwighaye, Kerisom t\u233? y\u233?n\u233? tuk sifayat y\u233?n\u233?rsam \u225?nde y\u233?nd s\u233?nonjo y\u233?nmakai. A y\u233?nd f\u233?yotaroe m\u233?ghm\u233?ghaf\u233? n\u233?ngretam k\u233?t\u233? s\u225?i y\u233?n\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ndimbal kwayaghayan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Y\u233?nd \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233? y\u233?n\u233?m m\u233? njam y\u233?nd t\u233?kratan y\u233?n\u233?m. Y\u233?nd mat y\u233?n\u233?m nden\u233? t\u233?kratam t\u233?funang\u233? awamarogh, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
awamarogham yanote im\u225?ng\u233?ghyam a im\u225?ng\u233?ghyamam eny\u225?tote t\u233?fene m\u233?ghm\u233?gh awanjargh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?ghm\u233?gham yau so tiny\u225?tong\u233? sotot y\u233?nd. Y\u233?nd mat y\u233?n\u233?m nder\u233? uw\u233?gh y\u233?nd y\u233?nmuwetam, m\u233?nam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? y\u233?nmaramai Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i tawafotau t\u233?fene tik\u233?f y\u225?ne uw\u233?ghe.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Y\u233?nd njam m\u233? t\u233?nmorw\u233?n muyafnar w\u225?ut\u225?r\u233?gh\u233?t y\u233?ndro, Keriso y\u233?nmorm\u233?n m\u233? y\u233?n\u233? efghonfifi a k\u233?r y\u233?morm\u233?n t\u233?fe yaufiyam \u225?r\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
T\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r yau so em s\u225?i k\u233?r em mbark\u225?nd \u225?roe, ndemam\u233?n \u225?mb \u225?r m\u233?t\u233? t\u225?f m\u233?nde y\u233?m s\u225?i k\u233?r y\u233?m \u225?rot efe y\u233?m minde mer. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
W\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yuyafotam y\u225?njo ndimbal uw\u233?gh t\u233?fefaf m\u233?naye y\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?retam Keriso m\u233?n\u225?t k\u233?r s\u225?i t\u233?morw\u233?n t\u233?feyot t\u225?f yaufiyaman m\u233? st\u233?nmorw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?nmumyoi nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? mbark\u225?ndro y\u233?maf\u233? y\u225?njo f\u233?rke. Y\u233?nd f\u233?yotaroe mat y\u233?n\u233?m y\u233?mon so t\u233?nmanjarng\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene n\u233?kwta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Y\u233?mon t\u233? y\u233?ny\u225?toi f\u250?tar Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? y\u225?njo ambumoene k\u233?r k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? t\u225?f y\u233?nd m\u233? njam t\u233?nmorw\u233?n y\u225?ne m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r. S\u233?nonjo y\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene f\u250?tar y\u233?n\u233?m, y\u225?njo Ambumom f\u233?yotaroe so t\u233?nmanjarng\u233? y\u225?njo gh\u233?rsaye. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? yau y\u233?m m\u233?inyotio! Y\u233?nd minde n\u225?uwetam s\u233?nonjo m\u233?nam\u233?n n\u233?m\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? yafrotam t\u233?feyot. T\u233?fene Yur\u233? Yesu Kerisom t\u233? yafrotam y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?yotaroe. Y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?m m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u225?nem\u233?n nden\u233? y\u233?nd t\u233? s\u233?nonjo n\u233?n\u225?y\u225?tong\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene f\u250?tar.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 K\u233?r Ed\u233?mene k\u233?nj\u250?n, gh\u233?rs\u233? Kerisoene k\u233?nj\u250?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Yaufiyam n\u233?nyawai mband maratot \u225?mbiro \u225?r k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?, a y\u225?ne yaufiyamam y\u233?n\u233?rsam k\u233?r. Y\u233?n\u233? ende, k\u233?ram m\u233?inyotio \u225?r yanai, m\u233?nam\u233?n m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?m yaufiyam nufrotam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Soram\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam n\u225?k eramai fronde yaufiyam t\u233?morw\u233?n mband maratan. W\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? efghon, Ng\u225?nj\u225?n yau nden\u233? norayai \u225?r k\u233?rtat so t\u225?kmangai, m\u233?nam\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? yau tamorw\u233?n n\u225?k y\u233?feyot waitogh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
W\u233?nde m\u233? k\u233?ram talimndau m\u233?inyotio \u225?r, k\u233?tam\u233? Ed\u233?mene efoghta k\u233?t\u225?n Mosesene efogh. M\u233?inyotio \u225?r k\u233?r emorm\u233?n, f\u225? w\u233?i efe yau nuyay\u233?nd nden\u233? endeyo Ed\u233?m snuyai.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Ed\u233?m siy\u233?m mbanmband y\u233?m \u193?r efe so y\u233?n\u233?m soram\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
W\u233?nde k\u233?t\u233? y\u233?m ndimbalfifi f\u233?nataye y\u233?fene n\u233?ndk\u233?fan Ed\u233?mene yaufiyam a Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ram\u233?ghm\u233?n ng\u225?r\u225?m. Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?mbiro \u225?r, Ed\u233?mene yaufiyamam y\u233?n\u233?rsam k\u233?r m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?t. W\u233?nde nder\u233? mindefifi Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ng\u225?r\u225?m a ram\u233?gh y\u233?morm\u233?n \u225?mbiro \u225?roene k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?, Yesu Keriso emon en\u233?rsam f\u233?nat\u233? ndimbalfifi freng\u233?gh m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
W\u233?ikor Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ram\u233?gh nden\u233? yau y\u233?m Ed\u233?mene yaufiyamm\u233?n fai k\u233?s y\u233?m. Ed\u233?mene yaufiyamam y\u233?limndam waghan\u233?ghfaf, w\u233?nde t\u233?feyot y\u233?na y\u233?m yuwek ram\u233?gh \u225?rk\u233? yumyote Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam, ndemam\u233?n y\u233?nd k\u233?rtaf\u233? y\u233?n\u233?m t\u225?rf\u225?r yaufiyamm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Ed\u233?mene yaufiyamam y\u233?n\u233?rsam k\u233?r, y\u233?n\u233? \u225?mbiro \u225?r k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?. Nder\u233? mindefifi emofem so tumyongi Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ng\u225?r\u225?m a y\u225?ne mbark\u225?nd yam ram\u233?gh, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?fe m\u233?inyotio emofem tanangi so emor y\u233?nayan waing\u233?gh yaufiyam a k\u233?r y\u233?n\u233? \u225?mbiro \u225?r k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?, Yesu Keriso.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
F\u233?yo, Ed\u233?mene yaufiyamam y\u233?n\u233?rsam k\u233?rtaf\u233? m\u233?inyotio \u225?rfefaf, w\u233?nde Kerisoene \u225?mbiro mbark\u225?nd yam wafrogham y\u233?n\u233?rse mbark\u225?nd f\u250?taryam y\u233?maf\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n a tot\u233?r gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u233?feyot m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n \u225?mbiro \u225?rom y\u233?kenai Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, m\u233?inyotio \u225?r n\u233?namnday\u233?nd yaufiyam \u225?r. W\u233?nde m\u233?nam\u233?n \u225?mbiro \u225?rom yiy\u225?rai Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, m\u233?inyotio \u225?r so mbark\u225?ndro t\u225?y\u225?tong\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ewaramai n\u225?k m\u233?n\u225?t yaufiyam narmboi. W\u233?nde \u225?nde yaufiyam narmboi, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ng\u225?r\u225?m narmboi minde ndimbal. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? yaufiyamam talimndai \u225?r k\u233?ran, s\u233?nonjo Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ng\u225?r\u225?mam y\u233?nlimnde nden\u225?ye, y\u233?nmaramete mbark\u225?nd okayogh Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? a y\u233?n\u233?rse y\u233?nd tuot gh\u233?rsat Yesu Keriso k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? t\u233?fene Yur\u233?.
