\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yaufiyaman k\u233?r w\u233?nde gh\u233?rs\u233? Kerisoene k\u233?nj\u250?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
\u193?mb \u225?r m\u233? t\u233? noraya, 'Y\u233?ndfem so m\u233? engwafrotam yaufiyam m\u233?n\u225?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ng\u225?r\u225?m m\u233? so narmbote.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Yaufifi! Y\u233?nd k\u233?r t\u233? y\u233?nmorm\u233?n yaufiyamta, ndern\u225?ye w\u233?i yaufiyaman m\u233? so y\u233?ng\u233?m? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
F\u233?m so mat em nden\u233? m\u233?inyotio y\u233?nd efe t\u233? y\u233?nm\u225?litotam\u233?nd Keriso Yesuene k\u233?nj\u250?t y\u233?nd nufnyay\u233?m y\u225?faf y\u225?ne k\u233?rfaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Y\u233?nd t\u233? y\u233?nyatotam\u233?nd y\u233?maf\u233? walitogh k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? y\u225?ne k\u233?rfaf m\u233?n\u225?t, nden\u225?ye Keriso y\u233?ngwano k\u233?rta Y\u225?refafene ndimbal muy\u233? k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?, y\u233?nd w\u233?i so y\u233?nmor tot\u233?r gh\u233?rsaye.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n njam y\u233?nd y\u233?maf\u233? \u225?mbiro y\u233?n\u233?m m\u233?rne y\u225?ne k\u233?r k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?, y\u233?nd w\u233?i nden\u233?yameyo so k\u233?rta nanotam nden\u233? f\u225? k\u233?s k\u233?rta nanoi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Y\u233?nd mat y\u233?n\u233?m nden\u233? t\u233?fene t\u225?nd\u225?w\u225?r fifioene m\u233?nde t\u233? enamndam\u233?ng wafatar\u233?gh w\u233?nan Yesuf\u233?. Y\u233?n\u233? nufrotam m\u233?n\u225?t fifioene m\u233?ndeyamam yau so y\u233?nlimnde yaufiyamot, a m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?nd ndenayu yau so y\u233?n\u233?m yaufiyamoene faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n \u225?rk\u233? \u225?r njam k\u233?r y\u233?m yaufiyamta t\u233? n\u233?kmbo.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
F\u233?yo, y\u233?nd njam t\u233? k\u233?r y\u233?morm\u233?n Kerisof\u233?, y\u233?nd nemnam nden\u233? y\u233?nd w\u233?i gh\u233?rs\u233? so y\u233?n\u233?m y\u233?maf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Y\u233?nd mat y\u233?n\u233?m nden\u233? m\u233?nam\u233?n Yesu k\u233?rta k\u233?s y\u233?ngwano, f\u225? w\u233?i yau so k\u233?r y\u233?m. K\u233?r waftafnar y\u233?ng\u233?m y\u225?faf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
