Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde, yau yumyotati yaufiyam s\u225?i elimnda f\u233?fene orng\u233?gh fifi m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?mofem s\u225?i ewaitotati yaufioene m\u233?nde. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
