K\u225?njo Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne, emo kwanjane tane k\u233?nj\u250?n Yesu Keriso t\u233?fene Yurane k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?!
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde, tane mwighaye y\u233?nd m\u233?nde w\u233?m s\u225?i ewaitotan Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene n\u225?k. W\u233?nde t\u225?fandio, w\u233?nde y\u233?ndo y\u225?s\u225?fotan yaufie nden\u233? tane yur\u233?, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd w\u233?m njang\u233?n a \u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 8
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Gh\u233?rs\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ran
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde, y\u233?feyot \u225?mb yau k\u233?rtaf\u233? y\u233?m efe em Keriso Yesuene k\u233?nj\u250?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n gh\u233?rs\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?roene n\u225?kam Keriso Yesuene k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? t\u233? yuwek tiy\u225?toi f\u233?m k\u233?tam\u233? yaufiyamoene n\u225?k a kroene n\u225?k. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? n\u225?k \u225?rk\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yaramai Mosese yau kor y\u233?ny\u225?toi y\u233?nd nden\u233? k\u233?s. Y\u233?nd t\u233?nmorw\u233?n muyafnar m\u233?n\u225?t waitogh\u233?t y\u225?ne n\u225?k m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd m\u233?nd \u225?r. W\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? yafrotam n\u233?m\u233? y\u225?ne n\u225?kam yau kor so tafrotau. Y\u233?mo y\u233?nmafaretam y\u225?njo Ambum s\u225?i n\u233?namndai \u225?r nden\u233? y\u233?nd siy\u233?n\u233?m. Y\u225?ne fifi t\u233?morw\u233?n nden\u233? \u225?r fifi emofem engwafrotat m\u225?m\u225?fi. Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene Ambum k\u233?r y\u233?morm\u233?n nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? gh\u233?ng\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i tawitau t\u233?krat yam t\u233?fene yaufiyamm\u233?n. Y\u233?n\u233? ende, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yironam yaufioene waft\u233? y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rfene efe em fifie muyafnar. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?n\u233? yafrotam m\u233?n\u225?t n\u225?koene m\u233?nde n\u233?mat y\u233?m so nufrotat t\u233?fefaf, efe yau emor yaufioene m\u233?nde wafroghyaman w\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r lim\u225?n\u233?ghan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
F\u225? efe elimnde yaufioene m\u233?ndeyamam nemnat m\u233? yaufi yamotro. W\u233?nde f\u225? efe emor Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ran nemnat n\u233?m\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r m\u233?nde y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Yaufioene m\u233?nde yamam y\u233?nlimndat k\u233?rot, w\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?roene mwigham y\u233?nlimndat gh\u233?rs\u233? a krufr\u225?t yamot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Yaufioene m\u233?nde yamaf\u233? t\u250?m\u233?n n\u225?sm\u233?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233?, m\u233?nam\u233?n yau ewaitote Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene n\u225?k, a yau f\u233?yotaro em waitogh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
F\u225? efe elimnd\u233? yaufioene m\u233?nde yamam yau y\u233?remngote Ng\u225?nj\u225?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
W\u233?nde f\u233?m yau elimnd\u233? yaufioene m\u233?nde yam, f\u233?m elimnd\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram, t\u225?f njam Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r y\u233?nyau f\u233?fefaf. Endefefaf yau y\u233?nyau Kerisoene Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r y\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?n yau em Kerisoene. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
W\u233?nde Keriso njam y\u233?nyau f\u233?fefaf, ndemam\u233?n f\u233?fene fifi k\u233?r so em yaufiyamm\u233?n, w\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram ewaramete gh\u233?rs\u233? f\u233?feyot m\u233?nam\u233?n Kerisom t\u233? mbark\u225?nd ey\u225?toi Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
A njam Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r y\u233?m f\u233?fefaf emo yanoi Yesu k\u233?rta, f\u225? emo yanoi Keriso k\u233?tam\u233? k\u233?rta w\u233?i so t\u233?ramang\u233? gh\u233?rs\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n f\u233?fene orn\u233?gh fififaf y\u225?njo Mb\u233?rmb\u233?re efe y\u233?nyau f\u233?fefaf.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n, tane f\u250?tar, y\u233?nd yau so y\u233?nmor s\u225?i y\u233?nremngota fifioene m\u233?nde yaman. Y\u233?nd yau so ndenau y\u233?nmor nden\u225?ye {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
F\u233?m njam emor fifioene m\u233?ndeye, f\u233?m so k\u233?r em. W\u233?nde njam Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?re krot t\u225?kmangi f\u233?fene yaufiyam wafrogh, f\u233?m so gh\u233?rs\u233? eng\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? efe elimnde Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram sem Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ambum. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
F\u233?mo yau y\u233?n\u233? mb\u233?rmb\u233?r yanai s\u225?i niy\u225?tota f\u233?rf\u233?raf\u233? w\u233?nde f\u233?mo yanai m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i n\u233?m Y\u225?ne ambum a Y\u225?ne k\u233?nj\u250?n y\u233?nd nutnam, "Af\u233?! Tane Af\u233?!" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram w\u233?i y\u233?monyo efalo yiy\u225?tote t\u233?fene mb\u233?rmb\u233?raf\u233? nden\u233? y\u233?nd si\u233?n\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r, y\u233?nd w\u233?i mat y\u233?n\u233?m nden\u233? y\u233?ndfem so tawinjong\u233?n mer rokar y\u225? tamb\u233?n. Y\u233?n\u233? rokar em y\u233?mon \u225?rk\u233? t\u233? uny\u233?ghofnar si ewaramai y\u225?njo ambumt\u233?rt\u233?rat. M\u233?rne y\u233?maf\u233? Keriso, y\u233?ndfem so tawanang\u233?m rokar \u225?rk\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? ewamnde y\u225?yot. Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m efalo t\u225?f njam y\u233?ndfem ey\u225?totam t\u233?krat yam nden\u233? Kerisom k\u233?s yafrotam. F\u233?yo y\u233?ndfem w\u233?i so yayamnetam gh\u233?rs\u233? njafaran nden\u233? Kerisom k\u233?s yafrote.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 S\u233?nonjo t\u233?krat a soramatau ndimbal kwayagh\u233?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Y\u233?ndon nemnan nden\u233? s\u233?nonjom\u233?n t\u233?kr\u225?t yamaf\u233? yau so katmang\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n soram\u233? ndimbal kwayagh\u233? s\u225?i nufrota t\u233?fefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
M\u233?inyotio rokar Ng\u225?nj\u225?n ewafrote nawanjete k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r so saf\u233?n t\u225?kmang\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
M\u233?inyotio rokar Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ewafrotam nawengoy\u233?nd fifiofnarot, yau m\u233?n\u225?yan y\u225?njo m\u233?ndeyan w\u233?nde m\u233?nam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene m\u233?nde t\u233?morw\u233?n. W\u233?nde k\u233?t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n m\u233?ghm\u233?gh, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
y\u233?n\u233? wafrogh rokar n\u233?retat k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?n\u233? efghot \u225?nde so kafghangi y\u233?fefaf Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne ambumt\u233?rt\u233?rafefaf ndimbal kwayagh\u233? k\u233?nj\u250?n yuwek k\u233?tam\u233? k\u233?rta orng\u233?ghta.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Y\u233?nd mat y\u233?n\u233?m nden\u233? m\u233?inyotio wafrogh rokar t\u233?kratan y\u233?m nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? ambum \u225?r\u225?fghan y\u233?nau t\u233?kr\u225?t y\u233?fandat y\u233?nanotio s\u233?nonjo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? w\u233?i y\u233?m nden\u233?yameyo t\u233?fe efe y\u233?n\u233?m efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r. Y\u233?ndfem t\u233? ewany\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? fronde y\u225?ne tamb\u233?n t\u233?feyot, w\u233?nde y\u233?nd w\u233?i nendam y\u233?ndo k\u233?nj\u250?m.Y\u233?ndfem t\u233? yanay\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? fronde ram\u233?gh t\u233?feyot, w\u233?nde w\u233?i y\u233?nd ye nendam t\u233?fenjo k\u233?nj\u250?n. Y\u233?nd nawanjetam y\u233?n\u233? efghot \u225?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so tifong\u233? y\u225?njo ndimbal \u225?s\u225?fogh. F\u233?yo y\u233?nd so y\u233?n\u233?m y\u225?ne f\u233?yotio nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u225?ne ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r. T\u233?fene fifi so em yuwek k\u233?tam\u233? yaufiyamoene waftata. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?ghm\u233?gh k\u233?nj\u250?n y\u233?nd t\u233? y\u233?nmanjay\u233?ng. W\u233?nde m\u233?ghm\u233?gh \u225?rk\u233? efandam y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?ghm\u233?gh siy\u233?m fifiofnar y\u233?m. Efe m\u233?ghm\u233?gh em y\u233?n\u233? rokarotio t\u225?f t\u233? ewam? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?nd njam m\u233?ghm\u233?gh y\u233?n\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? rokarfaf y\u233?ndfem \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? yau efandam, y\u233?nd nawanjetam y\u233?nat m\u233?tare.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? endeyo, Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram w\u233?i y\u233?nm\u225?ut\u225?ne t\u233?fene muyafnar sifayan. M\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd mafina y\u233?n\u233?m ndern\u225?ye so Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? norayam. W\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r f\u225?yo Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? norayet t\u233?feyot. F\u225? nutne Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf t\u233?fene t\u233?fnan y\u233?n\u233? ende \u225?r \u225?nde yau kor so noraye. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam efande n\u233?m\u233? em t\u233?fene tikfan, a f\u225? mat y\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? mwigh\u233? y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?roene, m\u233?nam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram noraye y\u225?njo \u225?r t\u233?fnan Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene m\u233?ndeyam\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
Y\u233?nd mat y\u233?n\u233?m nden\u233? m\u233?inyotio yaman Ng\u225?nj\u225?n n\u225?s\u225?fote merot y\u233?feyot emofem yuwetat f\u225?, efe t\u233? emotai y\u225?ne m\u233?nde wafrogh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n f\u225? mat y\u233?m t\u250?m\u233?n efe em y\u225?ne wafer\u233?ghkaf, y\u233?mon t\u233? mwigh\u233? y\u233?faronam f\u225? s\u225?i t\u225?y\u225?tongai ndenanit y\u225?njo Ambumnit, m\u233?n\u225?t y\u225?ne Ambum so k\u233?namndangai fronde s\u233?nko t\u225?rf\u225?r n\u233?ng\u233?nfefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? ewafery\u233?ng y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r s\u225?i em y\u225?ne ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r. Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan, y\u233?mo emote s\u225?i en\u233?m y\u225?faf. Y\u233?mo eumyote y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r nden\u233? mbark\u225?nd y\u233?maf\u233?. A y\u233?n\u233? efe eumyote, y\u233?mo w\u233?i em\u233?inde f\u225? so k\u233?namndangi ndimbal y\u233?tkw\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene uw\u233?gh Keriso Yesu k\u233?nj\u250?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
F\u233?yo, m\u233?nam\u233?n m\u233?inyotio yam Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam k\u233?s ewafrote t\u233?feyot, y\u233?nd so norayam nden\u233?: Njam Ng\u225?nj\u225?n t\u233? n\u225?s\u225?fota t\u233?feyot, \u225?rk\u233? \u225?rom yau so ewafrote \u225?mb yam t\u233?fe \u225?s\u233?nan\u233?gh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
Y\u233?mo efe yau yangoi y\u225?njo Ambum, w\u233?nde y\u233?nramai y\u225?njo Ambum k\u233?rot m\u233?inyotio t\u233?fe t\u233?fnan. Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so t\u233?nmarang\u233? m\u233?rne yane Ambumaf\u233? m\u233?inyotio rokar n\u233?m\u233? m\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
Efe \u225?r so noraye nden\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene \u225?r sem k\u233?rtaf\u233?. Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?monyo t\u233? y\u233?nmumyoi y\u233?nd nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? mbark\u225?nd y\u233?maf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
F\u233?yo efe yau so noraye nden\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so m\u233? t\u233?kratan y\u233?n\u233?kmete y\u233?nd. Efe yau. M\u233?nam\u233?n Keriso Yesu f\u225?yo t\u233? k\u233?r y\u233?morm\u233?n t\u233?fene t\u233?fnan. A Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yanoi gh\u233?rsat t\u233?feyot. S\u233?nonjo Keriso siy\u233?m y\u233?mor Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene tamb\u233?nta njafaran. F\u225? f\u225?yo Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf noraye t\u233?fene t\u233?fnan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
Emo so y\u233?nfalote y\u233?nd k\u233?tam\u233? Kerisoene uw\u233?ghta? F\u233?yotaro t\u225?ik\u233?ryam o k\u233?rt\u233? yamam o ngiyam o siogh o firoyam o k\u233?r kakayam o witmaf\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? n\u225?if\u233?? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
