Kerisoene fififaf. Y\u233?nd m\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233?m y\u225?ne \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r \u225?mbiro fifiyan, t\u233?feyot sem f\u233?natayero em \u225?s\u225?fogh wafrogh\u233?t, a nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?nd \u225?mbirofifi y\u233?n\u233?m Keriso k\u233?nj\u250?n, y\u233?nd y\u233?ndio so n\u225?frendam, a y\u233?ndfem m\u233?ndef\u233? so efandam \u225?mb \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
T\u233?fene em f\u233?natayero tamb\u233?n, y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?yotaro ng\u225?r\u225?m k\u233?s y\u233?nmaramai t\u233?fe. Njam \u225?roene tamb\u233?n noraya y\u233?n\u233? yam ufrogh\u233?t, so yafrotati y\u225?ne ndimbal mwigh\u233? f\u233?yotaroye {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
njam n\u225?s\u225?foghta \u225?r w\u225?ut\u225?rgh\u233?t so f\u233?t\u233? ew\u225?ut\u225?nati; njam y\u233?m watamegh\u233?t, so f\u233?t\u233? ewatametati. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Njam y\u233?m waw\u233?ngsogh\u233?t, so f\u233?t\u233? ewaw\u233?ngsotati. Njam y\u233?m ram\u233?gh k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rfene m\u233?nde n\u233?mat em, so f\u233?t\u233? tangwaram marataye. Njam y\u233?m lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?r ay\u233?m t\u225?ik\u233?r \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r. Njam gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? yuyafota, so yafrotati \u225?sneghaf\u233?.
