Njam y\u233?nd gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u233?n\u233?m, y\u233?nd gh\u233?rs\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?n\u233?m s\u225?i yut\u233?mndam Yur\u233?, a njam y\u233?nd k\u233?r y\u233?ng\u233?m, y\u233?nd so k\u233?r y\u233?n\u233?m Yuraf\u233?. Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde, njam m\u233? gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u233?n\u233?m o k\u233?r y\u233?n\u233?m, y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?m Yurane. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnanfifi, Keriso k\u233?r y\u233?morm\u233?n a nanoi gh\u233?rsat m\u233?n\u225?t f\u225? n\u233?namndai Yur\u233? k\u233?r \u225?rfet a gh\u233?rs\u233? \u225?rfet. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
F\u233?yo, f\u233?m, n\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?mo moghan ekmete fenjo f\u250?tar? O n\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?m n\u233?retati yuwon fenjo f\u250?tarefaf? M\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd m\u233?inyotio so kokayong\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mogh \u225?mnjogh kitarayan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Nden\u233? Buk si noraye,
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 "Yur\u233? noraye,'Y\u233?nd k\u233?s gh\u233?rs\u233? w\u233?m,
