Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde, y\u233?ndfem yau t\u225?f moghan ekmetam \u225?r ndenayu. W\u233?nde nemnati s\u225?i emor y\u233?n\u233? ende f\u233?mofem yau \u225?nde so yanawetati \u225?mb efalo y\u225?togh \u225?roe end. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m a saf\u233?nro y\u233?fandan Yur\u233? Yesuene waftaye nden\u233? njamkefaf yau y\u233?m m\u225?m\u225?fi n\u233?net, w\u233?nde \u225?mb \u225?r njam nemna nden\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi y\u233?m, f\u233?yo y\u233?n\u233? \u225?roe y\u233?m m\u225?m\u225?fi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Njam fene f\u250?tar\u233?m tanang sotot m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mo n\u233?m\u233? eneta, f\u233?m yau kor n\u225?s\u225?fota uw\u233?ghan. Yau m\u233? fene njamke n\u233?nem\u233?nro yas\u233?rmbotati fene f\u250?tar endeyot Keriso k\u233?r y\u233?morm\u233?n! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde yau t\u225?f yumyotati f\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? nemnati nden\u233? mer em y\u233?nam\u233? \u225?r k\u233?s norayat nden\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi kar em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n lim\u225?n\u233?gh yau y\u233?m njamke n\u233?neye a nu, w\u233?nde mbark\u225?nd yam, krufr\u225?t a \u225?uw\u233?gh Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r k\u233?nj\u250?n, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
m\u233?nam\u233?n emo njam yiy\u225?tota Keriso nden\u233? yam wafrogh y\u233?m \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne a \u225?r\u233?m w\u233?i efalo yiy\u225?tota.
