Yau yironati Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene \u225?s\u225?fogh m\u233? njamke t\u233?fnanro. M\u233?inyotio njamke sem mer, w\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi y\u233?m \u225?roe s\u225?i y\u233?neta y\u233?n\u233? njamke \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?nayam em\u233?inde \u225?mb \u225?r yaufiot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
