N\u233?m\u233? f\u233?mo njam efalo ey\u225?tota y\u233?n\u233? yamm\u233?n tan\u233? fenjo k\u233?nj\u250?t a Ng\u225?nj\u225?n k\u233?s. Freng\u233?ghkaf y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r y\u233?m efe f\u225?yo yau nawaghne m\u233?n\u225?yan n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mon taumyong\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
