M\u233?n\u225?t Keriso k\u233?nj\u250?n f\u233?m t\u233? namndangi wem\u225?r m\u233?inyotio rokar k\u233?nj\u250?n, y\u233?n\u233? efghangi m\u233?inyotio oray\u233?gh a m\u233?inyotio matyam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? si Kerisoenem\u233?n t\u233? efalo namndai f\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?n {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
nden\u233? f\u233?m yau n\u225?l\u225?itay\u233?nd umyogh\u233?t \u225?mbiro freng\u233?gh\u233?t, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u233?m kawanjetati t\u233?fene Yur\u233? Yesu Kerisoe m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i kufarngai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Y\u233?mon so nden\u233?yameyo ewerete f\u233?m taikrataye k\u233?t\u225?notio yatogh, m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?m so em t\u233?fnofnar t\u233?fene Yur\u233? Yesu Kerisoene efghon. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n siy\u233?m ndimbal mwigh\u233? k\u233?r ro y\u233?m, emo emotai y\u233?maf\u233? f\u250?tar yamot y\u225?ne Ambum Yesu Keriso t\u233?fene Yur\u233?.
