Tane f\u250?tar\u233?f, m\u233?naye t\u233?fene Yur\u233? Yesu Kerisoene si muyaye, y\u233?nd n\u243?mn\u233?ndan m\u233?inyotio f\u233?fefaf m\u233?n\u225?t \u225?mbiro mwigh\u233? tiy\u225?tongi n\u233?m\u233? f\u233?m norayati, m\u233?n\u225?t k\u233?t\u233? yau so afalogh y\u233?m f\u233?fefaf. M\u233? m\u233?inyotio kafghangi \u225?mbiro mwigh\u233? aem, a \u225?mbiro emarghaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Tane f\u250?tar\u233?f, \u225?mb \u225?r k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? Kloene m\u233?rnam waufroy\u233?nd ta nden\u233? m\u233? saf\u233?nro k\u233?t\u233? em \u233?wigh yam f\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?ndon nden\u233? ende so t\u233?kman, \u225?mbiro\u225?mbiro \u225?r\u233?m norayat f\u233?natayero. \u193?mb noraye, "Y\u233?ndon yaitotan Fol," \u225?mb, "Y\u233?ndon yaitotan Afolos," \u225?mb, "Y\u233?ndon yaitotan Fit\u233?", a \u225?mb "Y\u233?ndon yaitotan Keriso." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Keriso t\u233? t\u233?falotati m\u233?r\u233?nm\u233?rnot? W\u233?t Fol yamay\u233?nd wafatar\u233?gh w\u233?nan f\u233?feyot? N\u233?m\u233? f\u233?m ewalitotam\u233?nd Folene y\u233?tkw\u233?nan? Yau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u233?ndon k\u225?njo yarametan Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne nden\u233? y\u233?ndon efe \u225?mb yau ewalitotam\u233?n m\u233? Krisfus a Gaius, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
f\u233?yo efe \u225?mb yau so noraye nde f\u233?m n\u233?maritotamend tane y\u233?tkw\u233?nan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
(N\u233?m\u233?w\u233?t, y\u233?ndon nden\u233?yameyo yalitotam\u233?n Stefanas a y\u225?ne m\u233?r\u233?n, w\u233?nde y\u233?nd yau nawafrotan t\u233? o yau y\u233?ndon t\u233? namalitotam\u233?n efe ndafi.) {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Kerisom yau kw\u233?m\u225?f\u225?rete y\u233?nd walitogh\u233?t. Y\u233?mon kw\u233?m\u225?f\u225?rete y\u233?nd mer si s\u225?i nafrotan yau \u225?rfene matyam sie, m\u233?n\u225?t Kerisoene k\u233?r wafatar\u233?gh w\u233?nan yau so sotro tiy\u225?tongi y\u225?njo waftata.
