Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u225?njo k\u225?fet\u233? mwigh\u233? k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? yafrotam t\u225?ik\u233?r \u225?r\u233?t y\u225? wayamngong\u233?t m\u233?naye fai y\u233?fenjo k\u225?fet\u233? mwighaye. W\u233?nde m\u233?naye "fifiofnar" sie y\u233?ndfem kafrotam, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam mwigh\u233? yaitotam y\u233?fe gh\u233?rs\u233? urtogh\u233?t emofem efalo yiy\u225?toy\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Ju \u225?r m\u233?nde em s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? yam ufarogh\u233?t, a Grik \u225?r n\u233?retat k\u225?fet\u233? mwighat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
W\u233?nde nden\u233? t\u233?feyot siy\u233?m, y\u233?ndfem marataye si yaitotam Kerisoenem\u233?n efe y\u233?namndam\u233?nd, y\u233?n\u233? si siy\u233?m n\u233?t\u233?r Ju \u225?rfet a T\u233?ndo \u225?rfet siy\u233?m fifiofnar, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
w\u233?nde y\u233?fe siy\u233?m efe Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? emotay\u233?ng, s\u243?mbio m\u233?r\u233?n Ju \u225?r a T\u233?ndo \u225?r, y\u233?n\u233? si siy\u233?m Keriso, efe y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene waft\u233? a Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene k\u225?fet\u233? mwigh\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Mbandm\u233?n \u225?r t\u250?m\u233?n nemnat ndene Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene emar\u233?gh y\u233?m fifiofnar, w\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene emargham ewainde mbanm\u233?n \u225?rfene emar\u233?gh, a n\u233?m\u233? nden\u233? n\u233?rete Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene njang\u233?nnjang\u233?n kar y\u233?m, w\u233?nde y\u225?ne wafroghyam \u225?rk\u233? em minde muyaf\u233? ewainde \u225?rfene muy\u233?.
