Tane f\u250?tar\u233?f, kawafarotangi n\u233?m\u233? f\u233?m tamorw\u233?n njam Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam emotay\u233?ng f\u233?m. K\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? \u225?rfene matyam wafroghta t\u225?rf\u225?rofnar f\u233?m em k\u225?fet\u233? mwighaf\u233? o waft\u233? k\u233?r ro o tuk\u233?n y\u233?tkw\u233?naf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
W\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam takafang\u233? mwighafnar rokar y\u233?n\u233? mbandm\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t w\u225?iw\u225?iot s\u225?i t\u233?kmang\u233? matyam t\u233?fn\u225?r, a y\u233?mon takafang\u233? muyafnar rokar y\u233?n\u233? mbandm\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t w\u225?iw\u225?iot s\u225?i t\u233?kmang\u233? muy\u233? k\u233?r ro \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
Y\u233?mon takafang\u233? yuwan rokar y\u233?n\u233? mbandm\u233?n a kenaghkaf rokar a y\u233?n\u233? rokar \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? yau em m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i tawirorngi y\u233?n\u233? rokar \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? mbandam nemne y\u233?n\u233? mer y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? sioene fifi nden\u233? y\u233?m efe yau so nawarmbote Ng\u225?nj\u225?n s\u225?fr\u233?re. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
W\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? n\u233?nmanai f\u233?m \u225?mbiro namnday\u233?nd Keriso Yesuf\u233?, a Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? yiy\u225?toi Keriso s\u225?i y\u233?m t\u233?fene k\u225?fet\u233? mwigh\u233?. M\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?t\u233? f\u225?, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?nd t\u233? y\u233?n\u233?kmai mbark\u225?nd y\u233?maf\u233? a y\u233?nd n\u233?namndang\u233?m nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar a y\u233?nmanjary\u233?ng. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
