Tane f\u250?tar\u233?f, y\u233?nd yau so norayan f\u233?fefaf nden\u233? \u225?rfefaftro y\u233?nd f\u233?t\u233? so norayan efe em Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ran, w\u233?nde y\u233?nd f\u233?t\u233? so norayan f\u233?fefaf nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u233?m kar em y\u233?n\u233? mbandm\u233?n, o nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? fasri Keriso k\u233?nj\u250?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Y\u233?ndon f\u233?t\u233? so emanjnam f\u233?m nono w\u233?kwre, yau t\u225?ik\u233?r njamkeye, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m yau afreng\u233?ghkaf y\u233?nat. Efalo y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?m, f\u233?m t\u233?f\u233? yau afreng\u233?ghkaf em y\u233?nat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m m\u233? emor nden\u233? y\u233?n\u233? mbandm\u233?n \u225?r. Njam k\u233?t\u233? y\u233?m waramnjagh f\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?n a f\u233?m namronati f\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?n. Y\u233?n\u233? yamam eufane nden\u233? f\u233?m em y\u233?n\u233? mbandm\u233?n. A f\u233?m emor y\u233?n\u233? mband matyame emor. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Njam \u225?mb f\u233?m koraya, "Y\u233?ndon yaitotan Fol," a \u225?mb, "Y\u233?ndon Afolos yaitotan,"f\u233?fene wafroghyam ndenanit y\u233?m mband \u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
N\u233?mnat mbark\u225?nde, efe y\u233?m Afolos? A efe y\u233?m Fol? Y\u233?nd siy\u233?nre m\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?rro, emofem f\u233?m elim\u225?nm\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?n efalo y\u225?toghfaf. Y\u233?ndfem \u225?s\u225?fogh yafrowam \u225?rk\u233? Yuram taramang\u233? y\u225? wafrogh\u233?t: {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Y\u233?ndon mbwe eitam\u233?n, Afolos w\u233?n nue ewasune, w\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?n t\u233?morw\u233?n emon t\u233?m\u233?indau w\u233?n anogh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Emon eite a emon nue ewasune n\u233?mndafi y\u233?n\u233? yau y\u233?m, w\u233?nde m\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nro, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?mon em\u233?inde w\u233?n anogh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
K\u233?t\u233? f\u233?nat\u233? yau y\u233?m y\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?n emon eite a emon nue ewasun\u233?. Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so fai \u225?mbiro ewafrowam y\u233?n\u233? \u225?s\u225?foghan ndern\u225?ye y\u233?mofem t\u233? tawafrowam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Y\u233?nd siy\u233?nre m\u233?rne \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r Ng\u225?nj\u225?neyot a f\u233?m sem Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ndau a Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene m\u233?ngo.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam waramai ta ng\u225?r\u225?m wafrogh\u233?t, y\u233?ndon tafrotan \u225?s\u225?fogh nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? k\u225?fet\u233? mwighaf\u233? m\u233?ngo ram\u233?gh \u225?r a s\u233?ras\u233?r taitan, a \u225?mb \u225?r\u233?m t\u233?u yarametat y\u233?n\u233? tuk\u233?n. W\u233?nde \u225?mbiro\u225?mbiro so f\u233?t\u233? nawarawenat ndern\u225?ye so m\u233?ngo y\u233?ramete. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u225?nd\u225?i t\u233? y\u233?kmai Yesu Keriso \u225?mbiro a m\u233? f\u225?ro s\u233?ras\u233?r, a yau \u225?mb s\u233?ras\u233?r so t\u233?kmang\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
\u193?mb \u225?r\u233?m so yarametat m\u233?ngo gole, silfaye o tuk\u233?n faim\u233?n w\u237?me s\u233?ras\u233?r tuk\u233?n, \u225?mb \u225?r\u233?m so yarametat w\u233?ne o yuse a tafaye. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
\u193?mbiro\u225?mbiro \u225?rfene \u225?s\u225?fogh s\u225?f so y\u233?fandat njam Kerisoene efogh kufarng\u233?. Y\u233?n\u233? efghon f\u233?sam so saf\u233?n ekmete \u225?mbiro\u225?mbiro \u225?rfene \u225?s\u225?fogh, f\u233?sam so eufote a tauyafong\u233? \u225?s\u225?fogh k\u233?mbun. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
T\u225?f n\u233?m\u233? t\u233? tamorw\u233?n ram\u233?ghan s\u233?ras\u233?r tuk\u233?n f\u233?s wakraran kinamong\u233?, m\u233?ngo ram\u233?gh \u225?rom fai so tanang\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
W\u233?nde fene \u225?s\u225?fogh njam t\u233? kakerne, f\u233?mo so y\u233?tarn\u233? w\u233?nde f\u233?m f\u233?myo t\u233? nawanjar, t\u225?f f\u233?m t\u233? nawanjar f\u233?s k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?.
