\u193?r emo y\u225?s\u225?fota y\u225?ne yurane \u225?s\u225?fogh f\u233?t\u233? so em ndimbal mwigh\u233? k\u233?r ro. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
