Tane emar\u233?gh siy\u233?m saf\u233?n, w\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? yamam yau efalo yiy\u225?tote nden\u233? y\u233?nd mbark\u225?nd w\u233?m. Yuramro kwafrote mogh y\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
F\u233?yo f\u233?mofem yau yafrotati mogh \u225?mb \u225?rfefaf t\u225?f mbark\u225?nd efogh wufar\u233?gh frondeta. Nawanjeta f\u233?fene wifoghm\u233?n mogh \u225?mb \u225?rfefaf k\u233?t\u225?notio Yur\u233? n\u233?nangota. Y\u233?mon so en\u233?rse kwayaghat n\u233?m\u233? atnogh y\u233?m kw\u233?fkw\u233?fan a yufarote \u225?rfene m\u233?nde tikfan. A f\u233?yo y\u233?mofem so ewinjetat Ng\u225?nj\u225?neta \u225?uw\u233?gh.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Tane f\u250?tar\u233?f, f\u233?fene t\u233?fnan y\u233?ndon t\u233? ewangen m\u233?inyotio yam Afolosefaf a y\u233?ndio, y\u233?ndfem s\u243?mbioyam ewafrow\u233?m f\u233?fe uf\u233?nman\u233?gh\u233?t, m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?m so w\u233?i notametati t\u233?fefafta oray\u233?ghoene k\u233?mbun, "T\u233?k\u233?m kaka n\u233?m\u233? n\u225?k efrotam\u233?nd." F\u233?yo f\u233?m efe yau so nawarmbotati \u225?mb \u225?roenem\u233?n a \u225?mb y\u233?karotati. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Emon f\u233?m ey\u225?to ndimbal \u225?mb \u225?r\u233?t. Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ewaramai n\u233?m\u233? m\u233?inyotio fene em. F\u233?yo, ndern\u225?ye f\u233?m so nawarmbotati, a ndenanit n\u233?m\u233? t\u233? fene em yau kar ram\u233?gh y\u233?m?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
F\u233?m t\u225?nd\u225?i m\u233?inyotio fene m\u233?ndef\u233? rokaraf\u233? t\u233? namndangi! F\u233?m nemnati f\u233?m w\u233?m\u225?r t\u233?m! F\u233?m t\u233? lim\u225?n\u233?gh y\u233?rnyangi t\u233?feyofnaye! Y\u233?nd m\u233?nde w\u233?m f\u233?m s\u225?i y\u233?m lim\u225?ng\u233?h \u225?r efaloe. F\u233?m njam t\u233?morw\u233?n, y\u233?nd so w\u233?i y\u233?n\u233?m lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?r a y\u233?ndfem f\u233?maf\u233? so y\u233?limndam m\u233?inyotio rokar. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Nden\u233? n\u233?rete tafaf Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? y\u233?nmaramai kerker sifay\u233? t\u233?feyot Yesuene muyaf\u233? \u225?r, ndenanit \u225?r t\u233?kmangi krot marat sifayan m\u233?n\u225?t m\u233?inyotio mband maratam a njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r\u233?m a \u225?r\u233?m so yafandat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Kerisoene t\u233?fnan y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?m fifiofnar, w\u233?nde f\u233?m em k\u225?fet\u233? mwighaf\u233? Keriso k\u233?nj\u250?n! Y\u233?nd njang\u233?nnjang\u233?n y\u233?n\u233?m, w\u233?nde f\u233?m em muyaf\u233?! Y\u233?nd kenagh \u225?r y\u233?n\u233?m, w\u233?nde f\u233?m eut\u233?mndat! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Y\u233?nanotio s\u233?nonjo y\u233?nd y\u233?nyota siogh a nuofnar, y\u233?nd siy\u233?n\u233?m s\u225?l\u225?me f\u233?nd\u233?rf\u233?nd\u233?r y\u233?nmawo, y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?smetat, y\u233?nd noyamndam k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? \u225?mb yu k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?mb yu. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
