\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m efalo y\u233?m f\u225? norayat nden\u233? "m\u233?inyotio y\u233?nd matyam y\u233?n\u233?m." W\u233?nde matyamam \u225?r y\u233?m\u233?inde tuktukot; w\u233?nde uw\u233?gh yamam \u225?r yarmbote {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
F\u225? efe nemnat nden\u233? f\u225? mat em nauyafote nden\u233? fla efalo yau mat em nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u225? so mat em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
W\u233?nde njam \u225?r uweta Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, f\u233?yo Ng\u225?nj\u225?n efaloe mat y\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
F\u233?yo m\u233?nam\u233?n njamke n\u233?nem\u233?n mewangfaf ram\u233?ghm\u233?n. Y\u233?nd mat y\u233?n\u233?m nden\u233? mewang siy\u233?m yau efalofifi ng\u225?nj\u225?n a k\u233?t\u233? siy\u233?m m\u233? \u225?mbiro Ng\u225?nj\u225?n y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Njam k\u233?t\u233? em t\u225?rf\u225?r "ng\u225?nj\u225?n" njafar k\u233?nj\u250?n o mbandan, a y\u233?n\u233? em t\u225?rf\u225?r "nj\u225?nj\u225?n" a t\u225?rf\u225?r "yur\u233?, " {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
w\u233?nde t\u233?feyot siy\u233?m \u225?mbiro Af\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? ende tamb\u233?n m\u233?inyotio rokar nufrotam\u233?nd a endeyot y\u233?nd naketam. A \u225?mbiro Yur\u233?, Yesu Keriso, ende k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? m\u233?inyotio rokar nufrotam\u233?nd, a ende k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? y\u233?nd naketam.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
W\u233?nde m\u233?inyotio \u225?r yau mat em y\u233?n\u233? matyam. \u193?mb \u225?r m\u233?nj t\u233? em mewangfaf s\u233?nonjo tawotio njam enetat nden\u233? s\u225?fot njamke y\u233?mofem y\u233?n\u233? m\u233? ewafarenat mewangoene njamke \u225?rk\u233? em; m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?fene emar\u233?gh siy\u233?m njang\u233?nnjang\u233?n, y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m m\u225?m\u225?fi ewayatote. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
W\u233?nde njamke yam yau so kaka y\u233?ny\u225?tote Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf. Y\u233?ndfem yau so ewaghnam n\u233?mndafi t\u225?f y\u233?ndfem yau njam enetam, y\u233?ndfem n\u233?mndafi mer yau so ewinjotam njam y\u233?ndfem njamke enetam.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Aya kor aem, yau eumyotati f\u233?fenjo yuwek yim\u225?ng\u233?gh f\u225? em\u233?inde efe njang\u233?nnjang\u233?n ndimbal mwighayan nuitat yaufiyamot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Njam \u225?r endene emar\u233?gh y\u233?m njang\u233?nnjang\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? yaman k\u233?nminjong\u233? f\u233?m, endene matyam t\u233? y\u233?m, n\u233?n\u233?yan s\u225?i k\u233?nminjong\u233? mewang w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngon, y\u233?n\u233? yam so t\u233?m\u233?indang\u233? f\u225? njamke n\u233?net mewang ram\u233?gh njamket. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?n\u233? njang\u233?nnjang\u233?n \u225?r, fe f\u250?tar endeyot Keriso k\u233?r y\u233?morm\u233?n, so yaghne m\u233?nam\u233?n fene matyamm\u233?n! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
A y\u233?n\u233? ende f\u233?mofem so yaufiyam yafrotati Kerisoefaf m\u233?naye yaufiyam ewafrotati \u225?mb efalo y\u225?togh \u225?rfefaf a ewaghnati y\u233?fene njang\u233?nnjang\u233?n emar\u233?gh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
F\u233?yo njam njamke yam y\u233?m\u233?inde efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r yaufiyamot, y\u233?ndon yaufifi so y\u233?netan fenjen w\u233?ikor, m\u233?n\u225?t yau so y\u233?m\u233?indan efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r s\u225?i kuyang\u233? yaufiyamot.
