Y\u233?nd yuwek \u225?r w\u233?m. Y\u233?nd Yesuene muyaf\u233? \u225?r w\u233?m. Y\u233?ndon t\u233? yinjoy\u233?n Yesu t\u233?fene Yur\u233?. A f\u233?m em tane \u225?s\u225?fogh mbwe Yurai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
T\u225?f \u225?mb \u225?r\u233?m yau njam kumyongi y\u233?nd nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Yesuene muyaf\u233? \u225?r, y\u233?nd m\u233? f\u233?t\u233? w\u233?m f\u233?feyot! M\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m em tane faghar\u233?ghkaf em y\u233?nd w\u233?m Yesuene muyaf\u233? \u225?r.
