Njam \u225?r\u233?m waruindat y\u233?nd, y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m nden\u225?ye y\u233?nd naw\u233?marotan y\u233?ndio. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Tane mbark\u225?nd y\u233?m njamke a nu n\u233?net m\u233?nam\u233?n tane \u225?s\u225?foghm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Y\u233?nd mbark\u225?nd w\u233?m efalo y\u225?togh amaf wasrogh\u233?t y\u233?ndf\u233? tane \u225?lighan, ndenanit \u225?mb Yesuene muyaf\u233? \u225?r, Yurane y\u225?nngn\u233?f a Fit\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
A Banabas a y\u233?nd w\u233?i mbark\u225?nd y\u233?nre yau \u225?s\u225?fogh\u233?t gh\u233?rs\u233? \u225?mnjoghm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
N\u233?m\u233? fiyar\u233? n\u225?s\u225?fotat y\u233?fenjo fai k\u233?mgh\u233?t \u225?sm\u233?gh m\u233?r\u233?n k\u233?nj\u250?n? N\u233?m\u233? ndau t\u233?fn\u225?ram yau so enete g\u233?reif mbwe k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? y\u225?njo g\u233?reif mbwe m\u233?nj ndauta? N\u233?m\u233? sif wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?r\u233?m etrone nono k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? y\u233?fenjo sifta?
