Y\u233?nd yau norayan \u225?r mwighata y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?inyotio efogh wafrogh yamm\u233?n, m\u233?nam\u233?n n\u225?kam noraye nden\u233? yam m\u233?n\u225?yo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Y\u233?ndfem yaftam Mosesene n\u225?k k\u233?nj\u250?n nden\u233?, "Yau yumbeta kau s\u233?nf\u233?neyan njam etumnda flaw\u233? mbwe." N\u233?m\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n mwigh\u233? y\u233?m kaum\u233?n? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Efalo f\u225? noraye y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n t\u233?fefaf. F\u233?t\u233? y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?farotam\u233?nd t\u233?feyot m\u233?nam\u233?n emo njam y\u233?tana a emo njam eita so y\u233?fenjo \u225?s\u225?fogh yafrotat y\u233?n\u233? mwighayan nde y\u233?ndfem so \u225?mb tawanang\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? njamke. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Y\u233?ndfem t\u233? eitam\u233?m mb\u233?rmb\u233?re mbwe f\u233?fefafm\u233?. N\u233?m\u233? mindefifi t\u225?f y\u233?ndfem tatanam fifie rokar f\u233?fe tamb\u233?n? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
T\u225?f \u225?mb \u225?rfene t\u233? ewam mbark\u225?nd wamarogh\u233?t k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? f\u233?fe tamb\u233?n, t\u233?fene mbark\u225?nd siy\u233?m minde ndimbalfifi.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 W\u233?nde y\u233?ndfem yau yaman y\u233?kmang\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? mbark\u225?nd. W\u233?nde y\u233?ndfem yumyoy\u233?m m\u233?inyotio m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?nd yau so n\u233?t\u233?r y\u233?n\u233?m Kerisoene mer sifaf.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
F\u233?m mat em nden\u233? y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r efe n\u225?s\u225?fotat w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngon so ersat njamke k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? y\u233?n\u233? w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngota a f\u225? emofem erametat gh\u233?ng\u233?n kitarayan n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mofem ersat gh\u233?ng\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?ndio. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Nden\u233? endeyo, Yuram t\u233? y\u233?n\u233?mnday\u233?ng nden\u233? f\u225? emofem mer si yaitotat y\u233?mofem so tawanangi y\u233?fenjo gh\u233?rs\u233? \u225?mnjogh\u233?t k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? mer sita.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?nd yau tane mbark\u225?ndan k\u225?s\u225?fotan. A y\u233?ndon y\u233?n\u233? yau y\u233?farotan s\u233?nonjo m\u233?n\u225?t ewatnan tanjo mbark\u225?nd tandio. Y\u233?nd so k\u233?r w\u233?m fronde! \u193?rk\u233? \u225?rom yau so tengong\u233? tane mbark\u225?nd fifiofnarot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Njam y\u233?ndon yaitotan mer si, y\u233?nd f\u233?yotarofnar awarmbogh\u233?t w\u233?m, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd naneghan si waitogh\u233?t. Nder\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi y\u233?m tayot njam y\u233?ndon yau yaitotan mer si! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Njam y\u233?ndon m\u233? tafrotan tanjo m\u233?ndeye, f\u233?yo y\u233?nd k\u233?ma kawanjetan faiot, w\u233?nde y\u233?ndon tafrotan y\u233?n\u233? \u225?s\u225?fogh m\u233?nam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? yumyoi y\u233?n\u233? \u225?s\u225?fogh tafaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
N\u233?m\u233? fai so y\u233?ndon tanan? M\u233? y\u233?naro y\u233?m: Mer si yafroghro y\u233?nd so karaman faiofnaye, a yau so tafrotang\u233?n tane mbark\u225?nd nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? mer si waitogh \u225?r.
