Y\u233?nd w\u233?m yuwek \u225?r, \u225?rk\u233? \u225?roene yau, w\u233?nde y\u233?nd n\u225?y\u225?totan y\u233?ndio m\u233?inyotio \u225?rfene faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r m\u233?n\u225?t t\u225?rf\u225?ram so efalo tiy\u225?tongi mer si. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Njamandio y\u233?nd n\u225?s\u225?fotan Ju \u225?rf\u233?, y\u233?nd ndenanit so w\u233?mor Ju \u225?rnit m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?mofem so efalo tiy\u225?tongi mer si, ndemam\u233?n y\u233?nd y\u233?ndio yau so Mosesene n\u225?k mbanmbanan w\u233?m. Y\u233?nd nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? so w\u233?mor ndern\u225?ye y\u233?nd w\u233?m, njam y\u233?nd n\u225?s\u225?fotam y\u233?maf\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?mofem efalo so tiy\u225?tongi mer si. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Nden\u233? ende, njam T\u233?ndo \u225?rf\u233? y\u233?nd yanmor ndenanit T\u233?ndo \u225?r k\u233?s em, Ju \u225?rfene n\u225?k t\u233?ndota, m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?mofem efalo so tiy\u225?tongi mer si. Y\u233?n\u233? yau nden\u233? y\u233?m nden\u233? y\u233?ndon yau Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene n\u225?k n\u225?y\u225?retan, y\u233?nd efalofifi sw\u233?m Kerisoene n\u225?k mbanmbanan w\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Muyafnar \u225?r\u233?t y\u233?nd k\u233?n\u225?y\u225?ton muyafnar m\u233?n\u225?t muy\u225?fnar \u225?r s\u225?i ersan. Y\u233?nd m\u233?inyotio yamam\u233? wafny\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t \u225?mb \u225?r wanjargh\u233?t Kerisoene sie.
