F\u233?m mat em nden\u233? kembneyan t\u225?rf\u225?r w\u233?rse t\u233?fn\u225?ram sifay\u233? ersat w\u233?rset, w\u233?nde \u225?mbiro \u225?romro so tanang\u233? y\u225?njo fai tombem\u233?n. Ersati m\u233?nat s\u225?i tanangi fai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
M\u233?inyotio kembne t\u233?fn\u225?r osar\u233?ghan so keworng\u233? yuwot sotaf\u233? watamegh\u233?t. Y\u233?mofem y\u233?n\u233? yafrotati m\u233?n\u225?t so tanangi \u225?kiki \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? yau so nakete, w\u233?nde y\u233?ndfem yafrotam m\u233?n\u225?t so tanang\u233?m \u225?kiki \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? so nakete tuot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n y\u233?nd n\u233?rsan mbark\u225?nde k\u233?t\u225?n wifogh fufaf. Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan y\u233?nd w\u233?m fais\u233? \u225?sm\u233?gh \u225?rnit emon yau ewanete y\u225?njo utar\u233?gh \u225?sm\u233?gh muy\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Y\u233?ndon tanjo fifi t\u225?ik\u233?r yiy\u225?totan t\u233?kr\u225?te m\u233?n\u225?t so m\u233?inyotio y\u233?m awamaroghan, y\u233?ndio m\u233?n\u225?t yau so kolang\u233?n kembnet.
