Tane f\u250?tar\u233?f, Y\u233?nd m\u233?nde w\u233?m m\u233? kawafrotangi n\u233?m\u233? nufrotam t\u233?fene \u225?kiafefaf emofem Moses t\u225?itotaw\u233?t. F\u225? tamorw\u233?n m\u233?inyotio njafar kwamkwam warawer\u233?gh mbanmbanan, a m\u233?inyotio n\u233?f\u233?rmay\u233?nd merro F\u233?rkat Arakaf k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
