Y\u233?namayo watamegh sian, y\u233?ndon yau n\u225?uw\u233?tan f\u233?fefaf, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?fene \u225?umeng\u233?gham w\u225?wefnogh\u233?t yafrote minde t\u233?krat, w\u233?nde yau mer yafrote. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Fronde sifayan, y\u233?nd n\u225?y\u225?retan nden\u233? njam f\u233?m naumendat nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n, k\u233?t\u233? afalogh em f\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?nro, a y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?ndon efalo yiy\u225?totan \u225?mb m\u233? ewam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Yau mwigh\u233? d\u233?ud\u233?u em y\u233?n\u233? s\u233?no afalogh f\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?n y\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t f\u225? efe mbarkandan y\u233?m so saf\u233?nro kawinjongi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Njam f\u233?m naf\u225?ngotati m\u233?rne, y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m yau Yurane njamke yenetati. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Nden\u233? njamke n\u233?nean, f\u233?m \u225?mbiro\u225?mbirom f\u233?t\u233? so f\u233?fenjo njamke enetati, f\u233?yo \u225?mb \u225?r siogh em t\u225?fandio \u225?mb w\u233?riaf\u233? em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
F\u233?fene m\u233?ngo yau t\u233? ewam njamke n\u233?net a nu n\u233?net? O f\u233?m m\u233?nde em w\u225?iw\u225?iaf\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n yiy\u225?tote a f\u225? efe \u225?ronjaghan em? N\u233?m\u233? so y\u233?nd korayang\u233?n f\u233?fefaf? Y\u233?ndon so \u225?uw\u233?tan f\u233?m? Y\u233?ndon yaufifi!
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Y\u233?ndon yanay\u233?n Yurata y\u233?n\u233? watamegh y\u233?ndon \u225?rk\u233? yafnamoy\u233?n f\u233?fefaf. Yur\u233? Yesu, s\u233?mb\u225?ran f\u225? s\u233?n y\u233?rametam\u233?nd, ewanai f\u233?skaf flaw\u233? ndimbul, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
a k\u225?njo si yaramai Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne, y\u233?tfoi, norayai, "Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m tane fifi, \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m f\u233?feyot. Yafrotati awafarogh\u233?t tanem\u233?n." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Nden\u233? endeyo, s\u233?ite njamke n\u233?ne soram\u233? y\u233?mon kafusi yerai a emndai, "Y\u233?n\u233? kafusi siy\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene tot\u233?r \u225?rny\u233?gh f\u233?mof\u233?, yetetai tane f\u233?rke. Njam f\u233?mofem y\u233?n\u233? nu yenetati, wafarotati y\u233?nd."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Njam f\u233?mofem yenetati y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?skaf flaw\u233? a nu yenetati y\u233?n\u233? kafusita, f\u233?mofem yaitotati Yurane k\u233?rm\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?notio f\u225? n\u233?nangota. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
F\u233?yo t\u225?f \u225?rk\u233? \u225?r\u233?m Yurane f\u233?skaf flaw\u233? o nu yenetat y\u233?n\u233? kafusian y\u233?n\u233? ende yau ut\u233?mndat f\u225?, f\u233?m yaufi yafrote Yurane fififaf a f\u233?r\u233?kfaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
F\u233?yo mer y\u233?m f\u233?m so n\u233?wasufetati f\u233?myo fronde, f\u233?yo soram\u233? f\u233?skaf flaw\u233? a nu enetati k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? y\u233?n\u233? kafusita. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
F\u225? emofem enetat f\u233?skaf flaw\u233? a nu Yurane fifi awasufoghofnaye en\u233?rsat mogh y\u233?fendio. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
Nden\u233? t\u233?fnan t\u225?rf\u225?r f\u233?m em enjne a njang\u233?nnjang\u233?n, a t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r k\u233?r t\u233? emorm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
W\u233?nde njam y\u233?ndio fronde nawasufetam merk\u233?r\u225?ye, y\u233?nd yau so Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mogh mbanmbandan y\u233?n\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?nd y\u233?nmote t\u233?f\u233?l y\u233?nramete Yuram, m\u233?n\u225?t nden\u233? y\u233?nd yau so t\u233?nkmang\u233? t\u233?krat m\u233?rne y\u233?maf\u233? mband \u225?rf\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
F\u233?yo, tane f\u250?tar\u233?f, njam kufngongi m\u233?rne \u225?umeng\u233?gh\u233?t Yurane njamke n\u233?net, fronde nawanjenati \u225?mbiro\u225?mbiro \u225?rot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
T\u225?f \u225?mb \u225?r siogh njam y\u233?m, fronde y\u233?mon so enete njamke m\u233?ngon, m\u233?n\u225?t nden\u233? f\u233?m yau so Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mogh mbanmbanan em njam f\u233?m naf\u225?ngotati m\u233?rne. Nden\u233? \u225?mb yamm\u233?n, y\u233?ndon so t\u233?ngfrendang\u233?n t\u225?f y\u233?nd njam k\u233?naflen.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 12
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Fok k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?roeta
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Tane f\u250?tar\u233?f, s\u233?nonjo mwigh\u233? m\u233?nam\u233?n fokm\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?roeta.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Y\u233?nd m\u233?nde w\u233?m f\u233?m mat kamndangi efalo si y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
F\u233?m mat em nden\u233? njam f\u233?m m\u233? tamorw\u233?n T\u233?ndo \u225?r, f\u233?m talimndaw\u233?t a tawarsotaw\u233?t gh\u233?rsafnar mewangot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Y\u233?nd m\u233?nde w\u233?m f\u233?m so mat kamndangi nden\u233? \u225?mbiro efe yau Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram y\u233?limnde so korayang\u233? "Afalngogh y\u233?m Yesuefaf!" a \u225?mb yau so marataye korayang\u233? nden\u233? "Yesu siy\u233?m Yur\u233?, " t\u225?fandro Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram yau njam n\u233?limnda.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
K\u233?t\u233? em f\u233?nat\u233? s\u225?fot mb\u233?rmb\u233?re fok, w\u233?nde nden\u233?yameyo Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram ewaramete. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
K\u233?t\u233? em f\u233?nat\u233? \u225?s\u225?fogh, w\u233?nde nden\u233?yameyo Yurai n\u225?s\u225?fote. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
K\u233?t\u233? em f\u233?nat\u233? \u225?s\u225?fogh wafrogh\u233?t, w\u233?nde nden\u233?yameyo Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ewaramete fok m\u233?inyotio \u225?rfefaf, m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?fenjo \u225?s\u225?fogh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?roene waft\u233? nauyafote \u225?mbiro\u225?mbiro \u225?rfaf f\u233?nat\u233? ende m\u233?inyotio \u225?rfene merot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram yaramete \u225?mbiro \u225?roe k\u225?fet\u233? mwigh\u233? afoghkaf si, njamandio \u225?mb \u225?roe y\u233?n\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram yaramet matyam afoghkaf si. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
\u193?mb \u225?roe y\u233?n\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram yaramete ndimbal mwigh\u233?, nden\u233?yameyo \u225?mb \u225?roe y\u233?mon yaramete waft\u233? mer y\u225?togh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram \u225?mb \u225?roe yaramete waft\u233? s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? yam wafrogh\u233?t, \u225?mb \u225?roe yaramete fok Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene si wafroghm\u233?n, a w\u233?i \u225?mb \u225?r\u233?t, y\u233?n\u233? fok m\u233?n\u225?t mat s\u225?i y\u233?m f\u233?nat\u233? s\u225?fot mb\u233?rmb\u233?r. \u193?mbiro \u225?roe yaramete fok m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?nat\u233? s\u225?fot kank\u233? si oray\u233?gh\u233?t a \u225?mb \u225?roe fok yaramete m\u233?n\u225?t n\u233?m\u233? noraye kankaye y\u233?n\u233? si wafergh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m \u225?mbiro a y\u233?n\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ryo emo y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?inyotio yafrote \u225?s\u225?fogh nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u225? nemne, y\u233?mon ewaramete f\u233?nat\u233? fok \u225?mbiro\u225?mbiro \u225?r\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 \u193?mbiro fifi t\u225?rf\u225?r fifi kafeyaf\u233?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Keriso siy\u233?m ndenanit \u225?mbiro fifi, \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m t\u225?rf\u225?r kafeyaf\u233?, w\u233?nde m\u233? y\u233?m \u225?mbiro fifi, ndemam\u233?n yafrote f\u233?nataye kafeyam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Nden\u233? endeyo, m\u233?inyotio y\u233?nd, Ju \u225?r o T\u233?ndo \u225?r, faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r a yuwek \u225?r, t\u233? y\u233?nmalitotam \u225?mbiro fifi k\u233?nj\u250?t y\u233?n\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?re, a y\u233?nd m\u233?inyotio t\u233? y\u233?nramay\u233?ng y\u233?n\u233? \u225?mbiro Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?re nu n\u233?net.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Fifi f\u225?yo siy\u233?m yau yafrote m\u233? \u225?mbiro fifi kafeyam, w\u233?nde t\u225?rf\u225?r fifi kafeyam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Njam kafkaf korayang\u233?, "M\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd yau ng\u225?ng\u233? w\u233?m, y\u233?nd yau wafnyang fifiyan, " y\u233?n\u233? yam yau y\u233?kmbote kafkaf s\u225?i y\u233?m fifi kafe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
A njam t\u233?ngan korayang\u233?, "M\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd yau w\u233?m gh\u233?k\u233?f, y\u233?nd yau wafnyang fifiyan, " y\u233?n\u233? yam yau y\u233?kmbote t\u233?ngan s\u225?i y\u233?m fifi kafe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Njam m\u233?inyo fifi y\u233?m m\u233? gh\u233?k\u233?fro, ndern\u225?ye so n\u225?y\u225?rete? A njam m\u233? t\u233?nganro y\u233?m, ndern\u225?ye so nomnde? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ekmetam f\u233?nat\u233? kafe fifiyan y\u225?njo m\u233?ndeyan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Njam m\u233?inyotio m\u233? \u225?mbiro fifi kafe y\u233?m, \u225?nde y\u233?m fifi? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? k\u233?t\u233? em t\u225?rf\u225?r kafe w\u233?nde \u225?mbiro fifi.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
F\u233?yo, gh\u233?kfam yau so korayang\u233? ng\u225?ng\u233?faf nden\u233?, "Y\u233?nd m\u233?ndefnar w\u233?m f\u233?m!" Yau s\u233?nko so korayang\u233? kafkaffaf, "Mer, y\u233?nd m\u233?ndefnar w\u233?m f\u233?m!" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
At\u233?rar\u233?ghe, y\u233?ndfem yau so n\u233?m\u233? ewafrotam y\u233?n\u233? fifi kafeyofnaye \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? em njang\u233?nnjang\u233?nnit, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
a y\u233?n\u233? fifi kafem\u233?n nden\u233? y\u233?nd nemnam nden\u233? yau mer em w\u233?nde y\u233?ndfem \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? ewarawenam ndimbal k\u233?r\u225?ye, y\u233?n\u233? fifi kafe \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? yau mer n\u233?retat f\u233?nat\u233? utman\u233?gh, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
nden\u233? warawer\u233?gh yau y\u233?m minde mer fifi kafeyat. Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? fifi efghai y\u233?n\u233? ende nden\u233? s\u225?i ewarameta ndimbal utman\u233?gh y\u233?n\u233? fifiyat \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? fifiofnar n\u233?retat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
F\u233?yo k\u233?t\u233? siy\u233?m yau falogh y\u233?m fifiyan, w\u233?nde m\u233?inyotio f\u233?nataye fifi kafe \u225?mbiro\u225?mbiroe nden\u225?yo mwighaf\u233? nafandat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Njam \u225?mbiro fifi kafe kawambang\u233?, m\u233?inyotio \u225?mb fifi kafe w\u233?i kawambangi. Njam \u225?mb fifi kafe n\u225?uw\u233?ta, m\u233?inyotio \u225?mb fifi kafe \u225?uw\u233?ghan em y\u233?maf\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
F\u233?m m\u233?inyotio sem Kerisoene fifi, a f\u233?m \u225?mbiro\u225?mbiro sn\u233?m fifi kafe n\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n k\u233?nj\u250?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? ekmetam\u233?ng m\u233?inyotio y\u233?fenjo sifayan: fronde sifayan Yesuene muyaf\u233? \u225?r, y\u233?namayo sifayan Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r, a nambiom\u233?n sifayan watamegh \u225?r, f\u233?yo f\u225? emofem s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? \u225?s\u225?fogh ewafrotat, waft\u233? mer y\u225?togh\u233?t enjneta, o \u225?mb \u225?r w\u225?ut\u225?rgh\u233?t, o \u225?mb wambgh\u233?t o \u225?mb oray\u233?gh\u233?t f\u233?natayo kank\u233? sie. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Y\u233?nd m\u233?nyotio yau em Yesuene muyaf\u233? \u225?r, o Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r, o watamegh \u225?r. Yau m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?m so s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? yam ewafrotat, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
o m\u233?n\u225?t enjneta mer y\u225?togh\u233?t, o m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i norayat kank\u233? si, o m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i y\u233?fenat n\u233?m\u233? noraye. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
Tikfe t\u233?kwnat minde tuk\u233?n fok.
