Tane f\u250?tar\u233?f, y\u233?n\u233? fiy\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?ndon norayan. Njam f\u233?m naf\u225?ngotati m\u233?n\u225?t w\u225?wefnogh\u233?t, \u225?mbiro \u225?roene wagh so y\u233?m, \u225?mb \u225?roene watamegh\u233?t, \u225?mb \u225?roene so y\u233?m uyafogh\u233?t k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?neta, \u225?mb \u225?roene so y\u233?m kank\u233? sim\u233?n, a m\u233? so y\u233?m \u225?mb \u225?roene wafer\u233?gh\u233?t n\u233?m\u233? s\u225?i noraya. M\u233?inyotio yam so y\u233?m w\u225?ut\u225?r\u233?gh Yesuene m\u233?rnot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Njam \u225?mb \u225?r kufngong\u233? kankaye siot, s\u243?mbio o nambio \u225?mbiro\u225?mbiroero so norayat, a \u225?mb \u225?rom f\u233?t\u233? so y\u233?fene y\u233?n\u233? si. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
W\u233?nde njam yau k\u233?t\u233? y\u233?m emon so kank\u233? si y\u233?fene, f\u233?yo f\u225? efe noraye kank\u233? si f\u233?t\u233? m\u233? k\u233?kmbong\u233? Yesuene m\u233?rnan a noraya m\u233? y\u233?fefetio a Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Taumiy\u233?nd s\u243?mbio o nambio Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r oray\u233?gh\u233?t, njamandio \u225?mb \u225?r\u233?m ewaf\u233?nmetat n\u233?m\u233? si f\u225? norayat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
W\u233?nde njam \u225?mb \u225?r k\u233?t\u233? y\u233?mor \u225?umeng\u233?gh sifayan si Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam taramang\u233? y\u233?n\u233? \u225?mbiro efe noraye so k\u233?kmbong\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
M\u233?inyotio f\u233?mofem Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene si so nafrotati, \u225?mbiro\u225?mbiroero, m\u233?n\u225?t m\u233?inyotio \u225?r mat so ewatametat a w\u225?ut\u225?r\u233?ghaf\u233? so y\u233?m y\u233?feyot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene si wafroghm\u233?n \u225?rfene mb\u233?rmb\u233?r so y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?roene lim\u225?n\u233?gh mbanmbanan, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
m\u233?nam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?n yau m\u233?nde y\u233?m y\u233?nd s\u225?i yisramboghe y\u233?n\u233?m w\u233?nde afreng\u233?ghan a krufr\u225?tan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? m\u233?inyotio Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene \u225?r Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n k\u233?nj\u250?n, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
amaf m\u233?tar so ekmbotat Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n \u225?umeng\u233?gh k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?. F\u225? yau eumyotat oray\u233?gh\u233?t, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Ju \u225?rfene n\u225?k snoraye, y\u233?mofem yau so ersat sifay\u233? siot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
T\u225?f f\u225? njam m\u233?nde em \u225?mogh\u233?t matot, y\u233?mofem so emotat y\u233?fenjar\u233?f k\u233?t\u233? m\u233?ngon. Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m w\u225?iw\u225?iaf\u233? y\u233?m amafoe s\u225?i noraya Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n \u225?umeng\u233?gh k\u233?nj\u250?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
O f\u233?m nemnati nden\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene si y\u233?nmorm\u233?n f\u233?fe tamb\u233?n? O f\u233?mro f\u233?t\u233? em endefefafm\u233? y\u233?nmorm\u233?n? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
T\u225?f \u225?mb \u225?r njam nemna nde f\u225? siy\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r o Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?roene fokaf\u233?, f\u225? f\u233?t\u233? kawayamngong\u233? nden\u233? n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?ndon yafarotan f\u233?fefaf siy\u233?m Yurane si muy\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
W\u233?nde njam f\u225? yau m\u233?nde em s\u225?i yumyoi y\u233?n\u233? si, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yau so eumyoi f\u225?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
F\u233?yo, tane f\u250?tar\u233?f, yafarenati Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene si wafrogh\u233?t, w\u233?nde yau k\u233?kmbongi kank\u233? oray\u233?gh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
M\u233?inyotio yam miya ewafrotati merk\u233?raye a mbark\u225?ndero.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 15
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Kerisoene anogh
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
S\u233?nonjo, tane f\u250?tar\u233?f, y\u233?nd m\u233?nde w\u233?m mwighat f\u233?m so ewangotan mer sim\u233?n \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?ndon yaitotam\u233?n f\u233?feyot, \u225?rk\u233? f\u233?mofem y\u225?ney\u233?nd, a \u225?rk\u233? tuk\u233?n f\u233?fene ndimbal mwigh\u233? a yiyang nd\u233?rnd\u233?raf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? fiy\u233?m mer si y\u233?ndon yaitotam\u233?n f\u233?feyot. F\u233?m nawanjary\u233?nd mer sie njam f\u233?m m\u233? naweretati taikrataye y\u233?n\u233? sian-njam y\u233?n\u233? yau em, f\u233?fene efalo y\u225?togh so y\u233?m fifiofnar.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Y\u233?ndon yafnamotan f\u233?fefaf n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?ndon yumyoy\u233?n, \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m minde ndimbal yam: nden\u233? Keriso k\u233?r y\u233?morm\u233?n t\u233?fene yaufiyamm\u233?n, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Buk si noray\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
F\u225? t\u233? yiyatotam\u233?nd a t\u233? nanoy\u233?ng gh\u233?rsat nambio efogh k\u233?nj\u250?n, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Buk si noray\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
F\u225? nufary\u233?ng Fitafaf a k\u233?t\u225?n m\u233?inyotio 12 Yesuene muyaf\u233? \u225?rfefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233?, f\u225? nufary\u233?ng t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?rfefaf nden\u233? 500 efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r, t\u225?rf\u225?ryo gh\u233?rs\u233? m\u233? em, ndemam\u233?n \u225?mb k\u233?r emorm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233?, f\u225? nufary\u233?ng Jemsefaf, a w\u233?i y\u233?namayo m\u233?inyotio Yesuene muyaf\u233? \u225?rfefaf.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Soram\u233?fifi f\u225? nufary\u233?ng nden\u225?yo tafaf, \u225?mbr\u233?rero y\u233?nd w\u233?m nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? \u225?mb \u225?r endene \u225?r\u225?f\u233?gh yau mer y\u233?morm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Y\u233?nd n\u233?mbne w\u233?m m\u233?inyotio Yesuene muyaf\u233? \u225?rfeta, a f\u233?yotarofnar w\u233?m s\u225?i w\u233?motai Yesuene muy\u225?f\u233? \u225?r, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?ndon m\u225?m\u233?gh\u233?raye t\u233?smetaw\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
W\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ng\u225?r\u225?me y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?f w\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?nd w\u233?m, a ng\u225?r\u225?m y\u233?mon ta waramay\u233?ng yau t\u233?morw\u233?n fifiofnar. W\u233?nde tane wafroghyamam ewainde \u225?mb Yesuene muyaf\u233? \u225?rfene wafroghyam, w\u233?nde y\u233?nd yau n\u225?s\u225?fotan y\u233?n\u233? \u225?s\u225?fogh y\u233?nd y\u233?ndio. Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam f\u225?yo y\u233?ramete ng\u225?r\u225?m tafaf a w\u233?ramete y\u225?ne muy\u233? a f\u233?yo y\u233?ndon n\u225?s\u225?fotan y\u233?n\u233? \u225?s\u225?fogh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
F\u233?yo k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? ta tamb\u233?n o y\u233?fe tamb\u233?n y\u233?nmorm\u233?n, y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?y\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?ndfem m\u233?inyotio yaitotam a y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?y\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? f\u233?mofem efalo yiy\u225?totati.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 T\u233?fene anogh
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
W\u233?nde njam nden\u233? nafrotat nden\u233? Keriso t\u233? nanoy\u233?ng k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? k\u233?rta, ndern\u225?ye w\u233?t f\u233?m \u225?mb norayati nden\u233? k\u233?r \u225?r yau so nanotat gh\u233?rsat? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
T\u225?f efalo njam y\u233?m, y\u233?n\u233? fifi nden\u233? y\u233?m Yesu yau nanoy\u233?ng. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
A njam yau Keriso kanongai k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? k\u233?rta, f\u233?yo t\u233?fene si waitogh fifiofnar y\u233?m a nden\u233?yameyo f\u233?fene ndimbal mwigh\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
A y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?m tuk\u233?n nden\u233?, y\u233?nd nauyafotam nden\u233? nuindam Ng\u225?nj\u225?nenem\u233?n, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd norayam nden\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yanoi Keriso k\u233?rta. W\u233?nde njam y\u233?n\u233? efalo t\u233?morw\u233?n nden\u233? k\u233?r \u225?r yau nanoy\u233?nd gh\u233?rsat, t\u225?f nden\u233? y\u233?mon yau yanoi Keriso. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Njam yau k\u233?r \u225?r nanotat k\u233?rta, f\u233?yo Keriso yau kanongai k\u233?rta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Njam Keriso yau kanongai, f\u233?yo f\u233?fene ndimbal mwigh\u233? sof y\u233?m fifiofnar y\u233?m a f\u233?m w\u233?i sem m\u233? orsoghan f\u233?fenjo yaufiyan em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
A \u225?r efe efalo yiy\u225?totat Keriso a efe t\u233? k\u233?m\u233?gh n\u233?kakmetam\u233?nd nden\u233?yameyo orsoghan em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Njam t\u233?fene m\u233?ghm\u233?gh Keriso k\u233?nj\u250?n mer y\u233?m m\u233? y\u233?n\u233? gh\u233?rsatro, y\u233?ndfem so minde gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? tawinjong\u233?m y\u233?mofem efe m\u233?inyotio mband maratan em.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
W\u233?nde efalo si siy\u233?m nden\u233? Keriso t\u233? nanoy\u233?ng k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? k\u233?rta. Keriso y\u233?m fronde \u225?r f\u233?yo f\u225? efe k\u233?m\u233?gh t\u233? nakmetam\u233?nd, f\u225? nden\u233?yameyo so nanotat k\u233?rta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Nden\u233? k\u233?r y\u233?nmorm\u233?n \u225?mbiro \u225?r k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?, nden\u233?yameyo anogh k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? k\u233?rta so y\u233?n\u233?m \u225?mbiro \u225?r k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? m\u233?inyotio \u225?r k\u233?r k\u233?s em Ed\u233?mene k\u233?nj\u250?n, nden\u233? endeyo m\u233?inyotio \u225?r so nanotat gh\u233?rsat Keriso k\u233?nj\u250?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
W\u233?nde \u225?mbiro\u225?mbiro \u225?r so nanotat nden\u233?yameyo Keriso fronde, f\u233?yo y\u225?ne angoghan f\u225? efe y\u225?ne em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
F\u233?yo yatogh so y\u233?n\u233?m, Kerisom so tawaindang\u233? m\u233?inyotio mb\u233?rmb\u233?re lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?r, si muy\u233?, a waft\u233?, a so tafnamong\u233? lim\u225?n\u233?gh k\u233?t\u225?n Af\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Kerisom so yalimnde k\u233?t\u225?notio Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam tawaindang\u233? m\u233?inyotio m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r a f\u225? t\u233?kmang\u233? y\u225?ne kafkaf mbanmbanan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Soram\u233? m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r waing\u233?gh\u233?t siy\u233?m k\u233?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Buk si noraye, "Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ekmete m\u233?inyotio rokar y\u225?ne kafkaf mbanmbanan." M\u233? saf\u233?nro y\u233?n\u233? si k\u233?s em nden\u233?, "m\u233?inyotio rokar" yau k\u233?t\u233? yafnyang Ng\u225?nj\u225?n f\u225?yo, emon ekmete m\u233?inyotio rokar Kerisoene mbanmbanan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
W\u233?nde njam m\u233?inyotio rokar t\u233? ekmay\u233?ng Kerisoene lim\u225?n\u233?gh mbanmbanan, f\u233?yo f\u225? f\u225?yo, Ambum, kakmang\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mbanmbanan, emo ekmete m\u233?inyotio rokar y\u225?ne mbanmbanan, m\u233?n\u225?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?n so y\u233?m m\u233?inyotio k\u233?nj\u250?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
N\u233?mam\u233?n w\u233?t y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r efe ewalitote k\u233?r \u225?rfet? N\u233?m\u233? y\u233?fene m\u233?ghm\u233?gh y\u233?m ufrogh\u233?t? Njam y\u233?n\u233? efalo y\u233?m, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? \u225?mb norayat, k\u233?r \u225?r yau so nanotat gh\u233?rsat, n\u233?mam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r ewalitotam\u233?nd k\u233?r \u225?rfet? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
A t\u233?feyot siy\u233?m, n\u233?mam\u233?n y\u233?ndfem k\u233?rt\u233? y\u233?rsam m\u233?inyotio efoghf\u233?nef\u233?nen? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
