Njam y\u233?nd t\u233? nas\u233?mwam "munjan t\u233?krat w\u233?r\u225?raf\u233?" y\u233?na Efesos k\u233?nj\u250?n \u225?fr\u225?taye k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? \u225?rfene mwighata, n\u233?m\u233? mer y\u233?ndon so tanan? W\u233?nde njam k\u233?r \u225?r yau nanotat gh\u233?rsat, f\u233?yo, nden\u233? si k\u233?s yiyota, "Kamyong\u233?m njamke a nu n\u233?net, m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?nd k\u233?r so y\u233?n\u233?m k\u225?ye."
