Y\u233?ndon yafarotam\u233?n f\u233?fe y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?r\u233?n m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd m\u233?nde w\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i tawinjon nder\u233? mer f\u233?m tawakai y\u233?n\u233? ufogh yaman a t\u250?m\u233?n afreng\u233?ghkaf em \u225?y\u225?rgh\u233?t tane watamegh sifaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Njam f\u233?mofem tawalindangi \u225?roene yaufiyam n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mofem t\u233? tanwafrotat, y\u233?ndon w\u233?i tawalindangen. Njam y\u233?ndon tawalindangen, k\u233?t\u233? njam \u225?mb em walindang\u233?gh, y\u233?ndon yafrotan Kerisoene s\u225?fr\u233?re m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?fenem\u233?n, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?ndfem yau so sifay\u233? yarametam S\u225?if\u233?refaf. M\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd mat y\u233?n\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? S\u225?if\u233?roene mwigh\u233? a wafrogh y\u233?m nden\u233?.
