Y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?m Kerisoene m\u233?ndef\u233? wimaf\u233? w\u233?kw\u233?r Ng\u225?njanene s\u225?fr\u233?re, y\u233?maf\u233? efe t\u233? ewanjary\u233?ng a efe oling\u233?ghkaf tamorw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?m m\u233?ndef\u233? wimaf\u233? w\u233?kw\u233?r y\u233?feyot efe oling\u233?ghkaf tamorw\u233?n a m\u233?ndef\u233? wimaf\u233? gh\u233?k\u233?r y\u233?fefaf efe t\u233? ewanjary\u233?ng. Efe so f\u233?yotaro y\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? \u225?s\u225?fogh\u233?t? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Y\u233?nd yau y\u233?n\u233?m nden\u233? t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r k\u233?s y\u233?m, emofem Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene si yaitotat m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?fendio merot. Y\u233?nd nafrotam Ng\u225?njanene si efalo y\u225?togh k\u233?r ro a nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r.
