F\u233?m f\u233?myo em t\u233?fene f\u233?r\u233?n, t\u233? efarotam\u233?m t\u233?fene tikfan m\u233?n\u225?t m\u233?inyotio \u225?r matot a wafgh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m m\u233? saf\u233?nro nden\u233? Kerisom y\u233?monyo y\u233?farotam y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?r\u233?n a yatambang\u233?m y\u233?ndfemyo. Y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?r\u233?n siy\u233?m, yau kayogh w\u233?kwre w\u233?nde akegh Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene Mb\u233?rmb\u233?re, yau w\u237?m tuk\u233?n w\u233?nde \u225?rfene tikfan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Y\u233?nd norayam m\u233?nam\u233?n sotaf\u233? y\u233?n\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?n k\u233?nj\u250?n Keriso k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
