F\u225? y\u233?m emo t\u233?fe y\u233?naramay\u233?ng \u225?s\u225?fogh\u233?t tot\u233?r \u225?rny\u233?ghm\u233?n, \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?re, yau y\u233?m faroghe n\u225?ke m\u233?nam\u233?n faroghe n\u225?kam y\u233?n\u233?rse k\u233?r, w\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram y\u233?nmaramete gh\u233?rs\u233?.
