Y\u233?n\u233? n\u225?k t\u233?morw\u233?n faroghkaf f\u233?r\u233?n w\u237?man, a Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ndimbal kwayagh\u233? nufary\u233?ng njam y\u233?ramay\u233?ng. Ndemam\u233?n Mosesene s\u225?fan kwayagh\u233? kolindau, minde muyaf\u233? Israil \u225?r f\u233?yotarofnar tamorw\u233?n gh\u233?kfe fandagh\u233?t y\u225?faf. Njam n\u225?kam, \u225?rkam\u233?n\u225?yam y\u233?n\u233?rse k\u233?r y\u233?m wafareghan, y\u233?nmorm\u233?n ndimbal kwayaghaf\u233?, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
nder\u233? ndimbal kwayagh\u233? y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?roene \u225?s\u225?foghfaf! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Njam y\u233?n\u233? \u225?s\u225?fogham \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?n\u233?rse k\u233?rtaf\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n ndimbal kwayagh\u233?, nder\u233? ndimbal kwayagh\u233? \u225?s\u225?fogh y\u233?m \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?nayam y\u233?n\u233?rse mbark\u225?nd yam! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
N\u233?m\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n ndimbal kwayagh\u233? s\u233?nonjo yau ndimbal kwayagh\u233? y\u233?m njam y\u233?t\u233?mndam tot\u233?r ndimbal kwayaghaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
A njam t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n ndimbal kwayagh\u233? \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?morm\u233?n tekofnaye, nder\u233? ndimbal kwayagh\u233? y\u233?m \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? nakete tuot!
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n t\u233?fene y\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?ghm\u233?gh, y\u233?nd si\u233?n\u233?m mb\u233?nmb\u233?nate norayam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Y\u233?nd yau y\u233?n\u233?m nden\u233? Moses, emon so tafarngai s\u225?l\u225?meye y\u225?ne s\u225?f m\u233?n\u225?t Israil \u225?r\u233?m yau so tefandaw\u233?t kwayagh\u233? kawaindau a kolindau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u233?fene mwigh\u233? ewam d\u233?ud\u233?u, s\u233?nonjo taw\u233?tio y\u233?n\u233? efghon, y\u233?fene mwigh\u233? sem wafar\u233?ghkaf y\u233?n\u233? s\u225?l\u225?meyeyo y\u233?mofem njam yaftat t\u225?nd\u225?w\u225?r \u225?rny\u233?gh buk. Y\u233?n\u233? s\u225?l\u225?me so kit\u233?rmbong\u233? m\u233?n\u225?yero efalo y\u225?toghe Keriso. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Nden\u233? s\u233?nonjo, njam y\u233?mofem yaftat Mosesene n\u225?k, s\u225?l\u225?meyam m\u233? ewafne y\u233?fene mwigh\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
W\u233?nde njam \u225?rk\u233? \u225?r kawengong\u233? Yurafaf, y\u233?n\u233? s\u225?l\u225?me t\u225?f kafnarng\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Yur\u233? siy\u233?m Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r, a \u225?nde y\u233?m Yurane Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r, k\u233?t\u233? y\u233?m yuwek. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
M\u233?inyotio y\u233?nd, efe y\u233?n\u233?m so s\u225?f awafar\u233?ghofnar y\u233?lalam Yurane ndimbal kwayagh\u233?, a so ofnamoghe y\u225?n\u233? s\u225?ffaf armboghanro ndimbal kway\u225?ghaf\u233?, \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?n\u233?m Yurata, efe y\u233?m Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r.
