Njam mer si y\u233?ndfem \u225?rk\u233? t\u225?itotam t\u233?noghan y\u233?m, t\u233?noghe y\u233?m m\u233? y\u233?feta efe olingh\u233?ghkaf em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
S\u225?if\u233?r, efe y\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? mbandm\u233?n yaufi ng\u225?nj\u225?nam, mwigh\u233? kw\u233?fkw\u233?f ey\u225?totate efalo y\u225?toghofnar \u225?rfene, m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?mofem yau so y\u233?fandat mer sioene kwayagh\u233? \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?ramete Kerisoene ndimbal kwayagh\u233?, efe y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mbanmban. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Y\u233?nd yau nafrotam t\u233?fenjom\u233?n, w\u233?nde y\u233?nd nafrotam Yesu Kerisoenem\u233?n nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Yur\u233?, a y\u233?ndio nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u233?fene faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r Yesuene t\u233?fnan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, emo emndai, "Kw\u233?fitata kwayagh\u233? so n\u225?l\u225?lat, " y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?y\u233?m y\u233?nayo Ng\u225?nj\u225?n emon yafrote y\u225?njo kwayagh\u233? n\u225?l\u225?lat t\u233?fene tik\u233?fan, m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i y\u233?nn\u233?rse t\u233?fe matyam Ng\u225?njanene ndimbal kwayagh\u233? n\u225?l\u225?lat Kerisoene s\u225?fan.
