K\u233?t\u233? em t\u225?rf\u225?r m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r, w\u233?nde y\u233?nd yau f\u250?tarofnaye y\u233?n\u233?m, a m\u225?m\u225?fi y\u233?n\u233?m \u225?mb efghon, w\u233?nde y\u233?nd yau was\u233?rmboghkaf y\u233?n\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
M\u233?inyotio efghon y\u233?ndfem y\u233?rsam t\u233?fenjo fifie Yesuene k\u233?r, m\u233?n\u225?t nden\u233? Yesuene gh\u233?rs\u233? so y\u233?fandat t\u233?fene fifi k\u233?nj\u250?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
