Y\u233?n\u233? fifi nden\u233? y\u233?m k\u233?r siy\u233?m \u225?s\u225?foghan y\u233?m t\u233?fefaf, w\u233?nde gh\u233?rs\u233? siy\u233?m \u225?s\u225?foghan y\u233?m f\u233?fefaf.
