Buk si noraye, "Y\u233?nd norayan m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?ndo efalo yiy\u225?totan." Nden\u233? ndimbal mwigh\u233? mb\u233?rmb\u233?r k\u233?nj\u250?mayo y\u233?nd nden\u233?yameyo norayam m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?ndfem efalo yiy\u225?totam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u233?nd mat y\u233?n\u233?m nden\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, emo yanoy\u233?ng Yur\u233? Yesu k\u233?rta gh\u233?rsat, so nden\u233?yameyo t\u233?nmanong\u233? y\u233?nd Yesuf\u233? a t\u233?ngmang\u233?ng\u233? y\u233?nd m\u233?rne f\u233?maf\u233? y\u225?njo k\u233?nj\u250?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
