A Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, emon ewaramete mbwe y\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?rai a njamke n\u233?net, y\u233?mon so nden\u225?yo ewaramete f\u233?feyot m\u233?inyotio mbwe f\u233?m m\u233?nde k\u233?s em a so em\u233?inde anogh\u233?t a funagh\u233?t minde t\u225?rf\u225?r k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? f\u233?fene marataye ram\u233?ghta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Y\u233?mon so f\u233?m ey\u225?tote wem\u225?r f\u233?yotaro m\u233?n\u225?t marataye ram\u233?ghan em m\u233?inyotio efghon, m\u233?n\u225?t t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r\u233?m so k\u225?njo yarametat Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?fene ram\u233?ghm\u233?n \u225?rk\u233? t\u233?fe tamb\u233?nta ewinjongi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
