y\u233?ndon ewamnendan f\u233?mofem yau w\u233?m\u233?indati muyat njam y\u233?nd w\u233?n\u233?m. M\u233?nam\u233?n mat w\u233?m nden\u233? y\u233?ndon so yafrotan muyaf\u233? y\u233?fefaf efe norayat nden\u233? y\u233?nd n\u225?s\u225?fotam k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? mband maratoene mwighata. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
