Y\u233?n\u233? fimb y\u233?ndfem seweretam t\u233?fene \u225?sm\u233?gh k\u233?nj\u250?n yau y\u233?n\u233? em mband maratoene fimb, w\u233?nde Ng\u225?njanene waftaf\u233? fimb, \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? y\u233?ndfem eweretam m\u233?n\u225?t wirorgh\u233?t t\u225?ik\u233?r aw\u233?marogh sifay\u233?. Y\u233?ndfem ewironam uny\u233?gh amror\u233?gh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Y\u233?ndfem ewewonam yuwot m\u233?inyotio tuktuk yam \u225?rk\u233? nanote Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene matyam ngiot a y\u233?ndfem m\u233?inyotio mwigh\u233? ewangotam k\u233?t\u225?n Kerisoefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
A y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233? f\u233?m njam k\u225?y\u225?tongi efaloe, y\u233?nd so afreng\u233?ghkaf y\u233?n\u233?m t\u233?kratan k\u233?mgh\u233?t f\u225? efe n\u225?y\u225?retat.
