F\u233?m n\u233?retat faru rokaran. Efe naramangi f\u225?yo k\u233?t\u225?n Kerisoefaf? Mer, f\u225? so kemnangi w\u233?ikor y\u233?fenjom\u233?n, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd Kerisoefaf y\u233?n\u233?m nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u225? k\u233?s en\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Y\u233?nd yau w\u225?iw\u225?i w\u233?m, njam y\u233?nd tuktukan w\u233?m \u225?mbm\u233?n mindefifi m\u233?nam\u233?n muy\u233? \u225?rk\u233? Yuram y\u233?nmaramay\u233?ng t\u233?fe. W\u233?nde t\u233?fene muy\u233? eramai f\u233?fe tuk\u233?t, yau tirarai f\u233?fe yuwot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Yau nemnati nden\u233? y\u233?ndo kar f\u233?m f\u233?rf\u233?raf\u233? ey\u225?ton tane f\u233?rne. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
\u193?mb \u225?r so korayang\u233?, "Folene f\u233?r\u233?n sem k\u233?rtaye a muyaf\u233?, w\u233?nde njam f\u225? y\u233?m y\u233?na y\u233?ndf\u233? fifie, f\u225? siy\u233?m njang\u233?nnjang\u233?n a y\u225?ne si sem fifiofnar!" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Nden\u233? \u225?r so mat k\u225?y\u225?tong\u233? \u225?mb yau f\u233?nat\u233? y\u233?nayan y\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?ndfem y\u233?farotam t\u233?fenjo f\u233?rnan njam y\u233?nd yuk\u233?r y\u233?n\u233?m a n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?ndfem so ewafrotam njam y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?m k\u233?t\u233? f\u233?mof\u233?.
