Efaloe, y\u233?nd njam kemnaw\u233?n y\u233?ndo awarmbogh\u233?t tanem\u233?n, y\u233?nd yau so norayan ndenanit onon \u225?rnit, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd so norayan. W\u233?nde y\u233?nd nawewonan y\u233?ndio yau nawarmbotan. Y\u233?nd nemnan nden\u233? m\u233?t\u233? t\u225?f \u225?r nemnat tane sim\u233?n a tane efalo wafroghm\u233?n a f\u225? so norayat m\u233?nam\u233?n tane \u225?mb wafroghyamm\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? yau y\u233?mofem tafandat a y\u233?mofem so wuyotat a tane y\u233?tkw\u233?n so tuk\u233?n y\u233?m fifiofnar.
