Nambinotm\u233? y\u233?ndon Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? koraiwam Yurafaf y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n a y\u243?mnenday\u233?n f\u225? m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i tit\u233?rmbongai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
W\u233?nde y\u225?ne wangogh y\u233?morm\u233?n, "Tane ng\u225?r\u225?m siy\u233?m f\u233?yotaro y\u233?m feyot, m\u233?n\u233? tane waft\u233? siy\u233?m ndimbalfifi njam f\u233?m n\u233?m njang\u233?nnjang\u233?n." Y\u233?nd sw\u233?m mindefifi n\u225?uw\u233?tan, s\u225?i w\u233?m tuktukan tane njang\u233?nnjang\u233?nm\u233?n, m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?ndon so yay\u225?retan Kerisoene waft\u233? so n\u225?s\u225?fote tafaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Y\u233?nd n\u225?uwetan njang\u233?nnjang\u233?nm\u233?n, was\u225?lighm\u233?n, t\u225?ik\u233?r yamm\u233?n, ngim\u233?n, n\u225?uw\u233?ghm\u233?n Kerisoene t\u233?fnan. Njam y\u233?nd w\u233?m njang\u233?nnjang\u233?n, f\u233?yo y\u233?nd muyaf\u233? w\u233?m.
